name: Wellington Developments
description:
Wellington Developments is a forward-thinking real estate company based in Dubai, dedicated to shaping the future of urban living through innovation, luxury, and sustainability. Specializing in premium residential and investment properties, the developer is committed to crafting vibrant communities that meet the highest global standards. Every project is meticulously designed with cutting-edge architecture, smart technology, and eco-friendly solutions, ensuring an exceptional living experience while minimizing environmental impact.

With a mission to redefine real estate development, Wellington Developments focuses on delivering high-quality projects that foster community growth and offer strong investment potential. Strategically positioned in prime locations, their properties provide accessibility, convenience, and breathtaking views, making them ideal for homeowners and investors alike. By prioritizing excellence, sustainability, and customer satisfaction, Wellington Developments continues to set new benchmarks in the UAE’s thriving real estate market.

name: True Future
description: True Future is a real estate development company dedicated to creating thriving communities that blend modern innovation with timeless elegance. Each project is thoughtfully designed to enhance lifestyles, delivering a perfect balance of luxury, comfort, and functionality. Their commitment to excellence drives them to craft spaces that inspire, elevate, and endure. The company offers innovative spaces designed for modern lifestyles, integrating technology and convenience to enhance daily living experiences. They prioritize sustainable and environmentally friendly developments, utilizing high-efficiency materials to reduce carbon footprints. Additionally, their projects are strategically situated in prime areas, offering unmatched accessibility, connectivity, and vibrant surroundings.

name: Arete
description:
Arete Group creates architectural masterpieces that embody craftsmanship, clarity, and enduring character.

Delivering end-to-end real estate services—from concept development and engineering to construction, project delivery, and facility management—Arete blends innovative design with practical functionality, all while embedding sustainability and superior quality into every stage.

Guided by core values of excellence, sustainability, integrity, and customer-centricity, Arete ensures transparency and fosters trust throughout the investment and development journey, creating long-lasting value.

name: IQUNA Properties
description:
IQUNA Properties is a developer that treats every project as a deliberate statement — architecturally refined, emotionally resonant, and intelligently conceived. The company does not replicate but reimagines, believing that true innovation lies not in following trends, but in creating something original, lasting, and profoundly human.




Operating on a boutique scale with global ambition, IQUNA Properties combines design precision with long-term vision. Each development is intuitively functional, emotionally engaging, and architecturally sophisticated. At the core of the company’s philosophy is the belief that real estate should subtly elevate everyday living through intelligent design, thoughtful execution, and enduring impact.

name: Maakdream Properties
description: MAAKDREAM is the real estate brand of the future, born on the basis of the legacy of MAAKSONS Engineering Corporation Ltd. With over 70 years of experience in implementing megaprojects of national importance, MAAKDREAM was created to bring the same discipline, quality and further planning to the world of lifestyle development, starting with Dubai.Dubai is a city where innovation is combined with aspiration, and the appearance of MAAKDREAM means the beginning of a new chapter: chapters where engineering excellence is combined with architectural elegance.

name: Calgary Properties
description: Calgary Properties is a developer specializing in investment projects in Dubai. The company offers premium properties in the pre-launch stage, including apartments, townhouses, and villas. Their offerings are distinguished by contemporary design, high construction standards, and competitive pricing. Calgary Properties is focused on attracting investors seeking high returns and long-term capitalization.

name: Alaia Developments
description: We aim to encompass and elevate lifestyles, ensuring a seamless blend of luxury, sustainability, and quality.With over two decades of investment expertise in the region, Alaia Developments is focused on expanding its portfolio of luxury real estate, setting new benchmarks in design, craftsmanship, service, and elegance.

name: Avenew Development
description: Avenew Development integrates cutting-edge technology as a core element of its identity. The brand is dedicated to pushing beyond conventional boundaries, maintaining a forward-looking approach that anticipates future trends.

name: BlackSoil Real Estate Development LLC
description:
BlackSoil Real Estate Development is a visionary property developer based in the UAE, dedicated to shaping modern living through thoughtfully designed, community-oriented projects. With a clear focus on innovation, sustainability, and functionality, BlackSoil blends architectural elegance with practical design to create spaces that resonate with both investors and end users. The company is committed to delivering developments that not only reflect contemporary aesthetics but also enhance everyday life through quality, efficiency, and attention to detail.




Driven by a mission to redefine urban living, BlackSoil places people at the heart of every project. Their developments emphasize smart layouts, green spaces, and integrated amenities that foster vibrant, well-balanced communities. With a growing portfolio and a forward-thinking approach, BlackSoil continues to set new benchmarks in Dubai’s real estate market, delivering value-driven properties that stand the test of time.

name: Mr. Eight Development
description:
Mr. Eight Development is a European boutique real estate developer in Dubai, renowned for crafting exclusive, high-end homes that exemplify innovation and exceptional craftsmanship. With a focus on bespoke residences, Mr. Eight seamlessly blends architectural brilliance with Dubai's vibrant and evolving landscape. Sustainability and meticulous attention to detail are at the heart of every project, ensuring that each development offers not just luxury but also environmental consciousness.

The Mr. Eight Collection is driven by a philosophy that every building should embody a unique concept, each with its own distinct story and meaning. From visionary architecture to curated interior design, no two projects are alike. Every detail is thoughtfully designed to reflect the individuality and purpose of the building, creating spaces that are as extraordinary as the dreams that inspire them.

Mr. Eight is committed to achieving the extraordinary, turning the most ambitious visions into reality. Their mission is to create homes that are the physical embodiment of a dream, combining timeless elegance with cutting-edge innovation to offer unparalleled living experiences in one of the world's most dynamic cities.

name: ALAIN
description:
ALAIN is one of the UAE's premier asset management companies, renowned for its expertise across real estate, hospitality, education, and capital investment. 
They craft vibrant, sustainable residential, commercial, and mixed-use developments that uplift communities through purposeful design and long-term value. 
Their hospitality arm delivers award-winning, culturally rich experiences, while investments in education focus on empowering future leaders. Meanwhile, targeted capital investments span multiple sectors, driving economic growth through insight-driven, impactful strategies.

name: ARADA
description: Conceptualized with the intention of delivering superior properties to the UAE real estate segment, ARADA will pursue the development and timely delivery of projects. The newly-established company will draw on the vast experience of its founding parties and the breadth of their diverse commercial portfolios.Prospective residents and investors in the UAE and across the GCC will be presented with quality ARADA Living experiences and investment opportunities to own ergonomically designed homes. Building on existing corporate credibility, KBW Investments, and Basma Group have made the ARADA brand hallmark one of reliability, commitment to quality, and end-user value.

name: One Development
description: One Development is a homegrown boutique real estate developer dedicated to creating modern living spaces that foster a sense of community and connection. Our customer-centric approach ensures a unique and fulfilling experience for every resident.

name: Casagrand
description: Casagrand: Step into timeless comfort and refined luxury.Surround yourself with design that takes every detail into account, where your comfort is our priority, and privacy and exclusivity come together to make your stay a unique and authentic experience.

name: Nexus
description: We take a holistic approach to our projects, utilizing our full capabilities to ensure the best possible project execution. We have got apassionate team to deliver the best possible outcomes. At our core, we believe in fulfilling our promises and providing excellent products that our clients can trust and rely on for years to come.

name: Al Seeb Real Estate Development
description: Thanks to world-class service, first-class realtors and a firm belief that we can provide a wide range of research facilities at affordable prices, our professionalism and practical approach are embodied in projects that determine the future of real estate. Over the past 29 years, we have built a legacy based on the company's reputation for providing excellent services in residential projects, hotels, shopping malls and commercial premises.Embodying the vision of the parent company Al Safeer Group, a team of 3,500 professionals under the auspices of the founder, Chairman of the Board and CEO Mr. J.P. Kalwani provides unparalleled commitment.The portfolio covers retail, shopping malls, catering outlets, real estate, furniture, manufacturing, advertising, trade and much more. Guaranteeing value for money, the client's investments are secured thanks to our technical know–how, behind-the-scenes knowledge, marketing research and competitive prices.The development module includes luxury homes, hotels with the best value for money, consumer-friendly shopping malls and efficient commercial premises. A clear understanding of demand helps us create spaces that match the lifestyle of our employees. Rethinking the experience, each space is created to order with attention to detail, which makes it individual, warm and accessible.Every project that has cultural roots, is technologically oriented and passionately conceived, reaches the highest level of quality. From planning to brainstorming and, ultimately, implementation, El Sieb translates the future into the present.

name: CDS Developments
description: At CDS, we go beyond building structures, we create trust, comfort and belonging.Guided by global expertise, we’re here to redefine what living means in the UAE. Since 1999

name: RAK Properties
description: Established in 2005 under the visionary leadership of His Highness Sheikh Saud Bin Saqr Al Qasimi, Ruler of Ras Al Khaimah, RAK Properties is a testament to the future, with every detail meticulously crafted. Successfully launched flagship destinations including Mina Al Arab and Julphar Towers, garnering a solid reputation among shareholders. The company has undergone a transformation aligned with Ras Al Khaimah's robust Vision 2030. Their hallmark is creating communities that resonate with excellence, contemporary design, and nature's embrace, sculpting lifestyles for tomorrow's visionaries.

name: Arada
description:
Arada is a prominent real estate developer based in the UAE, known for creating master-planned communities that blend modern design with a strong focus on sustainability. Founded in 2017, Arada quickly established itself as a leader in the region by developing innovative projects aimed at providing high-quality homes and fostering a vibrant, inclusive community experience. The company’s flagship developments, such as Aljada and Masaar in Sharjah, showcase their commitment to smart urban living, incorporating green spaces, cutting-edge amenities, and convenient access to essential services.

Driven by a vision to create spaces that inspire and enhance quality of life, Arada emphasizes sustainable architecture and energy-efficient technologies. Their projects are designed to offer a balance between luxury and affordability, attracting a diverse range of residents. With a reputation for timely project delivery and customer-centric service, Arada continues to expand its portfolio, shaping the future of urban living in the UAE and beyond.

name: Confident Group
description:
Confident Group, the top real estate developer in South India, has expanded into the thriving Dubai property market, bringing its legacy of quality, trust, and innovation. With a commitment to excellence, the company now offers premium luxury homes, off-plan properties, and investment opportunities in Dubai, setting new benchmarks in the industry.




At the core of Confident Group's success are its cornerstone principles of superior quality and competitive pricing, which have garnered acclaim from both residential and commercial clientele. Priding itself on the timely delivery of projects, the company has consistently demonstrated a commitment to client satisfaction through punctual completions and impeccable finishings. Exclusively utilizing high-grade materials in all endeavors, Confident Group ensures that each development reflects a commitment to excellence, reinforcing its reputation for delivering nothing short of the finest craftsmanship.

name: AYS Developers
description: AYS Developers is known for their commitment to delivering exceptional customer service and ensuring customer satisfaction throughout the entire buying process, from initial inquiries to after-sales support. They also prioritize sustainability in their construction practices, using eco-friendly materials and technologies to reduce their environmental impact.

name: Object 1
description:
Object 1 is a distinguished member of the international TSZ Group, a prominent entity operating across real estate markets in Spain and the UAE. This innovative company is built on a foundation of collaborative minds, bold ideas, visionary strategies, diverse experiences, and shared ambitions. It is not just a developer but a creator of a modern urban aesthetic, crafting spaces that blend seamlessly with the demands of contemporary living, working, and inspiring.

With a strong track record of development excellence, Object 1 has become synonymous with quality and innovation in the real estate industry. The company is powered by a team of hundreds of highly skilled specialists operating across four key sectors: Development, Construction, Service, and Finance. This integrated approach ensures that every project is meticulously planned, executed, and managed, meeting the highest standards of quality and functionality.

Object 1 takes pride in its commitment to redefining urban environments by developing projects that enrich communities and provide unparalleled living and working experiences. From architectural elegance to sustainable construction methods, the company is dedicated to creating spaces that reflect the future of modern real estate while honoring the unique cultural and environmental contexts of its markets.

name: The 100
description: The 100 is a property developer that contributes to the development of Dubai through innovative and high-quality residential projects. The 100 is committed to creating residential complexes that meet the highest quality standards and meet the needs of modern residents.

name: C Fourteen
description: C Fourteen is a construction-related company operating in Dubai.

name: Arsenal East
description: Since 1997, Arsenal has been setting standards of luxury and comfort in Europe and the Middle East. Our projects are not merely real estate; they are inspiring spaces where every detail is crafted with quality and harmony.

name: Nshama Group
description:
Nshama is a Dubai based private developer and was established in September 2014. Nshama Properties offers high-class developments in Dubai and has delivered various mega developments such as the luxurious Arabian Ranches, Nshama Town Square, and Zahra Townhouses.

They created a major development in Town Square Dubai which features stylish homes surrounded by lush green spaces. Nshama takes green living to the next level. It will develop the outstanding community, designed with the next level technologies and will connect you online 24x7.

Nshama communities will empower creative living and entrepreneurship. Town Square launched by Nshama will offer an array of amenities such as hotels, cafes, health centers, restaurants, play areas, educational institutes, and much more. The community malls will be the ideal place for the friends and families to socialize and shop.

name: Major Developers
description: Major Developers is a distinguished name in the real estate landscape of Dubai, epitomizing excellence and innovation. Since its inception, the company has been committed to reshaping urban living through meticulously planned residential and commercial developments. Their projects are not just properties; they are vibrant communities designed to inspire and elevate lifestyles. With a focus on sustainability and modern aesthetics, Major Developers seamlessly blends cutting-edge technology with timeless design principles. Each project reflects the company’s vision of creating spaces that offer comfort, functionality, and a sense of belonging. From luxurious high-rise towers to serene community villas, their portfolio caters to diverse needs while maintaining the highest standards of quality and craftsmanship. Driven by a customer-first approach, Major Developers is known for its transparency, integrity, and a team of seasoned professionals who bring each vision to life. Their ability to innovate and adapt to changing market demands has earned them a reputation as one of Dubai's most trusted and forward-thinking developers.

name: DHG Properties
description: DHG Holding is an international real estate and construction group, founded in Zurich, Switzerland, in 1994. It has grown to manage operations in three countries: Switzerland, Serbia, and UAE, with real estate, development, construction, facility services, and finance. Organically grown with entrepreneurial foresight and insight, DHG Holding has a strong financial base and financial independence, maintaining the flexibility to seize investment and growth opportunities to further expand its market position in the future.

name: Tabeer Real Estate Development LLC
description: Dubai's trusted real estate developer for over ten years. Since our inception, we have specialised in the creation of high-quality, affordable residential spaces, and setting new standards for superior living experiences. Each development reflects our dedication to sustainable design, artistic expression, and groundbreaking ideas.

name: BNW Developments
description: From the majestic skylines of Dubai to serene suburban enclaves, BNW Developments projects epitomize elegance and exclusivity, tailored to meet the discerning tastes of their distinguished clientele. Like a bespoke suit, company tailor our services to fit investment parameters perfectly, ensuring clients real estate journey reflects their individuality. With this pioneering approach, BNW Developments able to introduce innovative strategies like Collaborative Investment Partnerships, Multi-Unit Investments, and other exclusive investment opportunities to the forefront.

name: DAMAC
description: DAMAC Properties is part of DAMAC Group that has been shaping the Middle East's luxury real estate market since 1982, delivering iconic residential, commercial and leisure properties across the region and beyond. Since the early days of DAMAC Properties, the organisation has continually received recognition and accolades for its contribution to the real estate development sector. Having now received over 100 global awards and commendations, for everything from high-rise architecture and interior design to excellence in hospitality and international golf course communities, DAMAC only goes from strength to strength. DAMAC Properties has grown to become one of the world’s foremost luxury developers, with projects spanning the GCC, Levant, Middle East, United States and United Kingdom.

name: MAK Developers
description: MAK, a visionary in Dubai’s real estate development combines design excellence and research insights to revolutionize the industry. Born from Al Hadaf Holdings, MAK crafts elegantly designed spaces, blending sophistication with functionality. With a foundation strengthened by seasoned industry partners, MAK is dedicated to fostering innovation, sustainability, and creating enduring, visionary projects that inspire and elevate modern living standards.

name: Segrex Development
description: Segrex Development has been developing exclusive projects in Dubai since 2015. The company is managed by a team of top managers with extensive experience in the construction and implementation of residential projects with a total area of ​​more than 500,000 sq.m. in Dubai and more than 1 Millions of square meters of luxury real estate.Among the successfully completed Projects in Dubai include over 20 premium private villas and residential buildings at JVC - "Astoria" and "Nicholas".Segrex Development is currently building three residential developments Stonehenge Tower 1 and Stonehenge Tower 2, Vitality Residence, scheduled for completion in 2025 and 2026.

name: Tasmeer Indigo Properties
description: At Tasmeer Indigo Properties, we're pioneering a new era of urban living tailored for today's generation. Our meticulously designed spaces offer millennials everything essential to thrive—modern amenities like co-working spaces, gyms, and dynamic community hubs. Beyond real estate, we're committed to cultivating connections, sparking creativity, and championing sustainable well-being. Join us in embracing an urban lifestyle crafted just for you—an experience that celebrates community, ignites innovation, and prioritizes your wellness.

name: Mr. Eight
description: For over 12 years, our team has been creating eco-systems and buildings that people truly want to call home. We have operated across Europe, and now, we’re expanding our reach, beginning our journey in Dubai.At Mr. Eight we believe that every building should embody a unique concept with its own distinct meaning. From architecture to interior design, every detail is meticulously curated to reflect the vision behind each project, ensuring that no two are ever the same.

name: Palladium Development
description: Company with a big history, experience in development and investment. Palladium Development delivers a total solution to all kinds of Real Estate projects, from initial concept through completion and handover to after sale maintenance and support.

name: Imtiaz Development
description:
Imtiaz Developments, established in the UAE in 2014, has quickly positioned itself as a leader in redefining the real estate landscape. With nearly two decades of experience through its construction division, the company goes beyond traditional development to create spaces that inspire and foster community integration. Their approach is deeply rooted in delivering value through innovative designs, functionality, and sustainable practices. Each project represents a bold step toward transforming urban living into an immersive and enriching experience, setting new benchmarks in the industry.

Guided by a visionary philosophy, Imtiaz Developments aims to create architectural masterpieces that stand as timeless symbols of creativity and ingenuity. Their mission to reshape living spaces revolves around blending artistry with practical sustainability, elevating lifestyles and redefining premium living. Imtiaz’s unwavering commitment to pushing boundaries ensures that their projects not only meet contemporary demands but also inspire a future where architecture and imagination seamlessly converge.

name: Emaar Properties
description: Emaar Properties is one of the world’s most valuable and admired real estate development companies. With proven competencies in properties, shopping malls & retail and hospitality & leisure, Emaar shapes new lifestyles with a focus on design excellence, build quality and timely delivery.

name: Azizi
description: Azizi Developments is a leading real estate and lifestyle developer in Dubai, UAE. The private company Azizi was founded in 2007 and has successfully developed and commissioned thousands of properties in various prestigious areas of Dubai. Azizi's main project locations include Al Furjan, near Expo 2020, Meydan (MBR City), near downtown Dubai, Dubai Healthcare City, Palm Jumeirah, Downtown Jebel Ali, Studio City and Sports City. Azizi is proud of its extensive portfolio of modern residential and mixed-use complexes strategically located in some of the most sought-after areas of Dubai. Applying a proactive, transparent and construction-oriented approach, Azizi strives to meet and exceed expectations by offering value for money and ensuring customer orientation.Azizi has a diverse local and international client base, including investors and end users (owner-occupiers), which cover more than 100 nationalities. Azizi's head office, located in the center of Dubai on Sheikh Zayed Street, employs more than 1,200 people representing more than 50 different nationalities. Currently, Azizi has about 100 ongoing projects to be implemented between 2021 and 2023, and more than 100 additional projects at the planning stage worth several billion US dollars, which are projected to be completed between 2023 and 2025. From value-oriented middle-income residential neighborhoods with shops and bed and breakfast establishments to luxurious coastal villages on Palm Jumeirah for the most discerning, Azizi offers a diverse portfolio for every taste and budget.

name: Damac
description: The private company DAMAC Properties has been operating in the residential real estate construction market in Dubai since 2002 as a division of the multidisciplinary enterprise DAMAC Group, founded back in 1982. DAMAC has been awarded numerous prestigious awards, in particular, as the best developer of the year. The number of objects transferred to the owners has almost reached 44 thousand, and over the past decade the pace of construction is only gaining momentum, which confirms the stable growth and reliability of the company.

name: Binghatti
description: Binghatti is a major Emirati property development company, based in Dubai. It is one of the largest property development companies in the United Arab Emirates. The company is renowned for being the UAE’s leading residential developer of a luxury mid-market segments and high-end homes.

name: HZ DEVELOPMENT
description: Al Helal Al Zahaby (HZ) is a distinguished real estate development company based in Dubai, United Arab Emirates, renowned for its commitment to excellence, professionalism, and ethical conduct in every transaction. The company's ethos is built on deep market knowledge, unwavering integrity, and a client-first approach, ensuring that each client experiences a seamless and transparent real estate journey. HZ aspires to be a reliable, one-stop destination that embodies modernity and world-class standards in professional real estate services. The company focuses on developing innovative concepts and solutions that exceed client expectations, delivering on promises made to business partners, stakeholders, employees, and the community. The mission of HZ is to create ideas, concepts, and sustainable living environments for a broad range of clients who wish to integrate design, architecture, and eco-friendly technology into their daily lives. The company strives to maximize investment returns while maintaining a strong business ethos based on ethics, integrity, sustainability, and a commitment to the environment and the communities in which it operates.

name: Object One
description: Our 10-year experience in construction has transformed into a great mission to create objects that will turn the city into a gallery of modern art.This is not only about the spectacular exterior, but also about the sensations inside each object."Being a head taller" is part of our philosophy. That's why we are building buildings where you can meet all your basic needs without leaving home. Each facility has areas for entertainment, sports, work and recreation with the whole family. We pay special attention to landscaping so that the whole environment inspires you and gives you a wonderful feeling.

name: Ellington
description: Founded in 2014, Ellington Properties is Dubai's leading design-led real estate developer and endeavours to craft beautiful properties and communities for high-quality lifestyles. A truly customer-centric developer in UAE, we develop beautiful residences designed by incredible artistry and impeccable architecture. Our customers’ refined tastes inspire us to create compelling luxury properties that consistently transcend fashions and trends.

name: Dugasta
description: Dugasta aims to become inseparable from notable ventures setting new norms for planning, craftsmanship, and propelling ways of life. With the current demand for high-quality projects in popular locations around the city of Dubai, Dugasta has a strong strategy, competence, financial strength, and is well-positioned to seize these exciting prospects while providing exceptional value to our clients. Mission - to create a legacy of excellence and customer satisfaction in the real estate market. They recognize the varying needs of their customers ranging from affordable housing to luxury developments and are committed to serving those needs without compromising quality.

name: Imtiaz
description: Over the last decades, the Asian and Middle Eastern economies have encountered various exhilarating and challenging phases with tremendous growth. We at Imtiaz Developments are proud to be a part of this magnifying business environment since 1993 and are determined to sustain our contribution towards the emerging markets and developing economies. Imtiaz Developments is strategically positioned to benefit from exciting global economic transitions.The fundamental pillars of our rich history of accomplishments remains in our experienced, professional and highly motivated team who strive to harness their diverse synergies in their fields. We work hard to push the human boundaries with innovation and superior quality services. The preliminary goal of our dynamic workforce is to embark on a strategic mission to efficiently meet the requirements of our clients, to empower them to achieve their business and financial goals.Our customer centric approach ensures that we build strong relationships with our partners and clients. We strive to understand their needs and deliver quality projects, on time and within the budget. We passionately believe that we offer a genuine point of difference from our competitors, whom have contributed enormously to our growth and success as an organization.We continuously refine our strategies to remain the world’s most valuable, most innovative and most admired company. Our ambition is to be an unstoppable organization that creates enormous value for our clients, our team, and our environment.

name: Meraas
description: Meraas is a Dubai—based holding company founded in 2007, which is one of the largest developers in the city. For the construction of buildings, Meraas applies innovations to ensure a comfortable life for the residents of Dubai.

name: Samana
description: Samana Developers is one of the fastest growing private developers in the country with their focus being on delivering the promise to each and every customer of a quality product at an appropriate price point that maximizes the returns for investors.

name: Tiger Properties
description: TIGER GROUP was founded in the year 1976 with an inspiring vision of the founders to effectively participate in the building of the United Arab Emirates through delivering landmark projects to the highest possible quality standard that exceed our customers’ expectations. Throughout our success journey, we expanded our businesses to include in addition to the Project Construction and Real Estate Development the Facilities Management, Hospitality, Manufacturing, Education and Health Care and extended our operational geographical zone to cover the Gulf Region, Middle East and Turkey.

name: Nshama
description: Nshama Company is a young, rapidly developing developer from Dubai, who is actively conquering the market and has earned a brilliant reputation as a reliable partner who always fulfills his obligations. The foundation date of the organization is considered to be 2014, when Fred Durie, who previously worked at Emaar International, decided to open his own business. He took the CEO's chair and went on a free voyage, implementing one grandiose project after another with enviable regularity.The flagship project of Nasa, through which the company publicly declared itself as a worthy competitor to the real sharks of the market, became Town Square Dubai. He is the personification of the whole concept of the developer — cozy houses and real communities of people united by common interests and the same views on life. If you need not just an apartment, but a real home – cozy, comfortable, with a soul and a twist – Nshama knows how to help you!

name: Nakheel
description: Based in Dubai, Nakheel is a leading global developer whose innovative, iconic projects form an iconic portfolio of master communities and residential, retail, hotel and leisure facilities that are crucial to realizing Dubai's vision. Nakheel's coastal projects, including the world-renowned, award-winning Palm Jumeirah, have added more than 300 kilometers to Dubai's original 70-kilometer coastline, paving the way for the construction of hundreds of beachfront homes, resorts, hotels and attractions.Nakheel's main developments cover 15,000 hectares, accommodate almost 300,000 people and provide a growing range of destinations, attractions and amenities for Dubai citizens, residents and tourists. These include Palm Jumeirah, The World, Jumeirah Islands, Jumeirah Park, Jumeirah Village, Al Furjan, Gardens, Discovery Gardens, Jebel Ali Village, Dragon City, Villas Over Al Shiba, Varsan Village, International City and Dubai Islands under construction - a new destination for tourism, life and leisure in the oldest, most traditional shopping mall in Dubai.

name: Vakson Development
description: Established in 1970, Vakson Development is a diversified business organization with deep roots in the UAE and a legacy of over 50 years. Headquartered in Dubai, the company has earned a trusted reputation in real estate and beyond. It offers comprehensive services in real estate development and investment, property management, facility management, construction, brokerage, valuations, and consultancy. Its vision is to be the region’s most respected and sought-after real estate partner, recognized for unwavering integrity, visionary leadership, and meaningful contributions to national development. Its mission is to deliver strategic, high-quality real estate solutions that generate lasting value for investors, stakeholders, and communities, while elevating the everyday experiences of its customers.

name: Reportage
description: With over 20 years of experience, Reportage Properties is one of the largest private developers in the United Arab Emirates, with projects in Abu Dhabi, Dubai, and now Egypt.We are focused and consistent in our objective to provide innovative, modern, and affordable housing solutions that not only offer our investors an outstanding value but also provide the home buyers a safe place to live in. We build homes with unparalleled elegance and comfort that redefine experiences.

name: Dugasta Properties Development
description: Dugasta Properties Development is a promising and evolving developer from Dubai, United Arab Emirates. Over more than 30+ years in the real estate industry, the Chairman and Founder of Dugasta Properties Development, Mr. Tauseef Khan is an expert in the Real Estate Market. Backed by the longstanding success of a prolific portfolio, Dugasta Properties Development is working towards providing its clients with high-quality and value-for-money projects. The company’s unique approach to business involves centering each development’s appeal on customer interests. Whether this means a plethora of investment options or easy payment plans, Dugasta has a wide umbrella of services to offer to property buyers.

name: HRE Development
description: HRE Development was originally established as a construction company and has evolved over the past 22 years into a premier real estate developer in the UAE. Backed by our in-house construction arm, we transitioned into real estate development three years ago, ensuring our projects are built with precision, efficiency, and purpose.

name: Tissoli
description: Tissoli is a collaboration of some of the finest minds in design, delivery, and operation, with a vision to become a leading aspirational lifestyle and design brand. The company focuses on creating world-class spaces that allow people to live life to the fullest, developing residences that not only symbolize modern living but also help transform communities. Its mission is to build vibrant neighborhoods where both people and communities can truly thrive, guided by a deep commitment to reimagining the consumer experience. For Tissoli, residences are envisioned as places with breathtaking views, surrounded by water, reaching toward the skies, where residents feel loved, pampered, and part of something iconic.

name: MAG Property Development
description: MAG Property Development is part of Al Gaddah (MAG) Group, a multinational conglomerate based in the UAE. With 40 years of experience, MAG Group is one of the largest corporations in the region, occupying a leading position among its colleagues in the field of real estate, contracting, engineering, industrial and commercial trade, freight transportation and hotel business. Today, MAG Property Development's interests range from innovative initiatives in the field of affordable housing and luxury projects to providing a health-oriented life in the UAE.

name: Cosmo Developments
description:
Cosmo Developments is a visionary real estate brand rooted in cultural heritage and elevated by intelligent design. From its inception, Cosmo set out not just to build properties, but to shape enduring legacies—creating spaces that honor the past while boldly defining the future. Every development is an expression of quiet strength and timeless refinement, designed for global citizens and forward-thinkers who seek more than luxury—they seek meaning, innovation, and sophistication in every detail.




Guided by a philosophy where design meets purpose, Cosmo Developments crafts environments that transcend trends and embrace permanence. Their approach blends architectural elegance with regenerative sustainability and cutting-edge technology, resulting in spaces that are not only visually stunning but also deeply intuitive and future-ready. With a commitment to creating seamless, soulful sanctuaries, Cosmo continues to raise the bar for modern living—shaping the future of luxury real estate in Abu Dhabi and beyond.

name: Dubai Investments Real Estate
description: Dubai Investment Realestate [DIR] is the real estate arm of Dubai Investments PJSC. Company has established its reputation through a distinctive portfolio of sustainable real estate solutions and today boasts of an impressive range of mixed-use developments, residential buildings, commercial projects including warehouses and land banks, across key strategic locations, providing an expansive portfolio to suit varied requirements.

name: Tomorrow World Properties
description: Tomorrow World is a boutique real estate developer established in 2022 in Dubai and is part of Tomorrow World Group, a leading trading conglomerate with a 20-year legacy (since 2002). The company focuses on premium residential projects, including developments on the Dubai Islands, with a strong emphasis on architectural innovation, sustainability, and high returns for investors.

name: Prestige One
description: Since 2007, Prestige has been a name at the forefront of Dubai Real Estate, with multibillion dirham investments, we have placed integrity, transparency and delivering on commitments at the heart of what we do. Prestige One Developments is a premier Dubai real estate developer focused on the customer, community and design for the discerning buyer and high-quality lifestyles.As a customer focused developer in the Dubai real estate market, we focus on residences where you can experience the design. From timeless architecture to tasteful interiors and superior amenities, our customers and the communities we shape, drive us to create luxury properties that consistently deliver to the most demanding of standards.We focus on locations and views as well, selecting the most prestigious communities with views that inspire and shape the design of the project.

name: Manodev Real Estate Development LLC
description:
Manodev is a Dubai-based real estate development firm focused on creating lifestyle-led residential communities that combine luxury, modern design, and seamless living. Their approach centers on delivering waterfront and resort-inspired developments that emphasize wellness, sophistication, and harmonious integration with the environment. Projects like ARKA Enclave reflect Manodev’s vision of offering more than just homes — they aim to craft sanctuaries where residents experience both tranquility and urban connectivity.




With a forward-looking pipeline, Manodev continues to expand its footprint across Dubai, positioning itself as a brand that values innovation, quality execution, and distinct architectural narratives. Operating from its base in Media City, the company aligns its developments with contemporary market demands and strives to deliver elevated living experiences through a blend of thoughtful design, premium finishes, and holistic community planning.

name: Wasl
description: Born from the vision to elevate Dubai's global prominence, Wasl was founded on May 25, 2008, with the mission to transform the city into an even more captivating destination for residents, businesses, and visitors alike. Created from the union of the Dubai Development Board and Real Estate Department, Wasl embarked on a journey of seamless integration. This strategic merger not only streamlined operations but also empowered our team with enhanced expertise, enabling us to adopt dynamic, market-driven investment strategies.Today, Wasl stands tall as a cornerstone of Dubai's real estate landscape. As one of the city's largest and most diversified real estate management companies, we proudly oversee an expansive portfolio of landmark assets, entrusted to us by DREC and other esteemed partners.

name: Beyond
description: BEYOND is a new developer of premium real estate, part of the OMNIYAT group of companies, which offers innovative solutions in the field of luxury housing construction. We strive to create homes where nature, luxury and modern technology combine. Our goal is to provide customers with not just a place to live, but a unique experience that will allow them to enjoy every day. We make every effort to ensure that all our facilities are delivered on time, and their design is thought out to the smallest detail. We create a space that meets the personal preferences of residents and improves their quality of life. From lush landscapes to cutting—edge technology, BEYOND offers a lifestyle in which every detail is thought out to the smallest detail. We strive to provide our residents with unparalleled comfort, convenience and well-being. Our mission is to go beyond expectations and create homes that inspire, uplift and match the modern lifestyle.

name: The Heart of Europe
description: The Heart of Europe is a heart–shaped archipelago consisting of 6 unique themed islands: St. Petersburg, Sweden, Switzerland, The Floating Venice, Germany and Main Europe. Each island will give you the opportunity to plunge into the culture of different countries and experience an unforgettable experience.The Heart of Europe Islands represent the quintessence of luxury beyond description and include luxury hotels, exceptional resorts, elegant villas and shopping areas. The Heart of Europe is an exclusive holiday resort, a great place for families, young couples and those who want to experience something new and luxurious.The project challenges the impossible, with the world's first climate-controlled resort, with artificial snow and rain and ancient relict Mediterranean trees over 1,500 years old imported from Andalusia in southern Spain, making it a truly magical place.

name: BT Properties
description: As Asia’s leading private real estate developer, Bahria Town (BT Properties) has spent 30 years transforming landscapes and shaping skylines with vision and expertise.Driven by a steadfast commitment to quality, we have delivered countless homes and developed extensive and significant infrastructure, elevating the standard of living for families while boosting local economies. Each development fosters stronger communities, creates jobs, and supports long-term urban growth.We transform ideas into iconic, master-planned cities that blend modernity with functionality. Every endeavour reflects our focus on fulfilling today’s needs while preparing for tomorrow. Through visionary planning and flawless execution, we have established ourselves as a trusted leader in urban development across Asia—and now, in Dubai.

name: Tebyan Real Estate Development Enterprises
description: Tebyan Real Estate Development Enterprises L.L.C is the consolidation of the track records and experiences of several major real estate investors and developers under one umbrella. The track record includes several hotels, residential, commercial, and entertainment projects in Saudi Arabia, Jordan, and Dubai.

name: Fakhruddin Properties
description: Fakhruddin Properties founded in 2003, is a renowned property development, property management, brokerage and hospitality management organization that offers end-to-end property solutions. We have steadily grown an international portfolio of residential and commercial projects in the UAE, the UK, and Uganda.We place a high priority on developing healthier living conditions for everyone, regardless of apartment size. Our residential spaces are all created with sustainability and environmental effect in mind, resulting in environments that help users minimize their carbon footprints on a daily basis. The buildings are designed with cutting-edge and intelligent automation technologies to maximize convenience while lowering energy usage, the use of solar and wind energy technology to meet energy demands is widespread and growing. We have a large property management portfolio, effectively serving a global clientele of investors with properties in the UAE. The dynamic business concept of Fakhruddin Properties International combines Real-Estate Development and Property Management in a unique method, resulting in favorable returns on investment for its clients.

description:
Radiant Real Estate is a leading Abu Dhabi-based developer known for delivering visionary residential and mixed-use communities that combine modern design, premium quality, and urban integration. The company’s projects—such as Radiant Square and Radiant Elite—are recognized for their strategic locations, panoramic views, and exceptional attention to both form and function.




Rooted in a philosophy of excellence, Radiant Real Estate brings together innovation, craftsmanship, and community-building. From luxurious residences with intelligent layouts to thoughtfully curated amenities that enhance everyday living, each development reflects the brand’s commitment to elevating standards in the UAE’s real estate sector. As part of its long-term vision, Radiant continues to shape the evolving skyline of Abu Dhabi with landmark projects that are both aspirational and enduring.

name: Atara Real Estate Development

With a vision rooted in innovation and lifestyle-driven concepts, Atara ensures every project reflects both sophistication and functionality. description: At Reef Developments, we are a pioneering developer in Dubai focused on transforming living spaces through innovative and practical solutions. description: It was back in 2016 when the first brick of the Iman Developers was laid, and since then we haven’t looked back. Focused on delivering premium properties and cultivating a vibrant community, the company offers more than just living spaces; it offers a vision of future living.
