description: Royal Centurion Real Estate Development is a construction-related company operating in Dubai. One of the well-known real estate developers in Dubai, who has established himself as one of the responsible developers in the Dubai real estate market through proper and consistent construction.

name: Irth Development
description: IRTH embodies the essence of legacy, anchoring its roots in the heart of a vibrant Dubai. As a part of a distinguished local family conglomerate, our privately held real estate investment platform draws strength from a heritage spanning over a century.At IRTH, our foundation is built upon three CORE values: Trust, Strength, and Agility. These principles serve as our guiding light, propelling us forward as a prominent player in the realm of real estate investment. We proudly stand among the elite establishments within the UAE, a testament to our unwavering commitment to excellence.Our influence extends even further through strategic partnerships with esteemed local and international hospitality brands, elevating our stature and enriching our portfolio. With an unwavering dedication to investment, IRTH paves the way for a diverse range of property ventures. Our footprint is set to expand both within the dynamic landscapes of Dubai and across international horizons. As we forge ahead, our legacy remains intertwined with the enduring values of trust, strength, and agility.The Alshamsi Family , the visionary founders behind IRTH, have sown the seeds of a legacy that continues to flourish. Our story is one of resilience, growth, and an unyielding pursuit of excellence.

name: Anax Developments
description: ANAX DevelopmentsAnchored in a strategic investment approach, we adhere to sound principles that guide our decisions, ensuring prudent and sustainable growth. Our customer focus is paramount, with a dedication to understanding and meeting the unique needs of each client. By harmonizing these elements, we not only navigate the intricacies of the financial landscape but also cultivate enduring relationships, solidifying our position as a trusted partner in the journey to financial success.Our brand narrative unfolds as a harmonious blend of passion, skillful craftsmanship, and groundbreaking innovation. Rather than merely constructing properties, we aspire to breathe life into dreams and aspirations, shaping them into tangible reality. Each home crafted by Elegance is a vibrant canvas, an artistic manifestation, and a living testament to our unwavering dedication to redefining the concept of affordable luxury.We’re resolute in providing unsurpassed services and a living experience that defines the essence of affordable luxury, setting the stage for your success and ours.

name: Vision developments
description: Your dream our commitmentAt Vision Developments, we are more than just developers; we are architects of dreams and creators of communities. From luxurious residential towers to commercial hubs, elegant villas our portfolio spans the spectrum of urban development. We believe in prioritizing our customers by investing in quality workmanship, superior products, and a skilled workforce, we ensure that every project we undertake exceeds expectations. Our commitment extends beyond affordability; we strive to deliver excellence in every aspect of our work. At the heart of our company lies a commitment to continuous improvement through a structured process of setting objectives, measuring results, and providing feedback. This dedication ensures that we remain at the forefront of the industry, setting new standards with every step of the way.

name: Dubai South Developers
description: When the Dubai Strategic Plan was unveiled by H.H. Sheikh Mohammed bin Rashid Al Maktoum, it sought to impress the importance of happiness upon Dubai’s population and empower its people to fulfil their ambitions. It’s from this vision that Dubai South was set out to create a community to foster innovation and entrepreneurship within a dynamic ecosystem, facilitating its role in propelling growth in the emirate’s economy. As a proud catalyst for Dubai’s macroeconomic performance, Dubai South established a framework that contributes towards the realisation of the emirate’s vision. By relentlessly working to enhance its competitiveness, Dubai continues to be a leader for innovation and transformation in its focused industries globally. Dubai South was conceived to align with Dubai Plan 2021, contributing towards the emirate’s continuous efforts for sustainable economic growth. This was facilitated through the creation of a business friendly environment to safeguard Dubai’s position as a preferred investment destination for business worldwide.

name: Green Group
description: Green Group is a sustainability driven & client focused real estate development company in Dubai, UAE. Using sustainable management in practice, Green Group is all about pioneering sustainability and innovation in real estate industry by building architecturally unique, striking and sustainable residential buildings and custom built villas.From the hand crafted wall panels to the plants carefully selected for the outdoor spaces, Green Group takes pride in an unparalleled attention to detail. Green Group brings their expertise to some of the finest addresses in the world. Each project is completed with an effortless marriage of design and functionality ensuring signature precision.Today, it’s not enough for the buildings we live in to be beautiful, big and bold. With climate change, a looming threat and the need for renewable energy sources becoming ever more pressing, residential apartments need to be green too.

name: Abou Eid Real Estate Development
description: Abou Eid Real Estate Development is a prominent and esteemed global leader in private development, renowned for its exceptional projects and innovative solutions. With a rich history spanning over three decades, the company has solidified its position as a reputable and trusted entity in the real estate market. Founded in 1989 in Lebanon, Abou Eid has expanded its reach and achieved remarkable success both domestically and internationally. The company’s pioneering efforts has made a lasting impact on the Middle Eastern markets through the introduction of the groundbreaking town houses, which has revolutionized residential offerings in the region. This commitment to innovation and forward-thinking has propelled Abou Eid to the forefront of the industry.

name: Palma Development
description: Palma Development is a subsidiary of Palma Holding. Thanks to its four support units: Palma Development, Palma Investment, Palma Real Estate and Palma Asset Management, Palma Holding offers unsurpassed, exclusive, customer-oriented services and individual development in Dubai's first-class real estate sector. Since its inception, Palma Holding has built over four million square feet of prime real estate in Dubai. The main activities of the group are Dubai Marina, The Palm, Business Bay, Burj Khalifa city center and other prestigious locations.

name: Taraf
description: Taraf is a boutique property developer and asset manager based in the UAE. With a unique approach to craftingdesign-led,high-quality properties.Taraf is reshaping the concept ofluxury living for its clients by offeringexclusivity and exceptional lifestyle opportunities in elevated living environments. A number of prestigious projects are currently under development and will be launching in 2023.

name: H and H Development
description: H&H Development was established in 2007 by Shahab Lutfi and Mohamed Al Hussaini. H&H offers, through its business divisions, a wide range of real estate related services, stretching from development into property management & leasing, facility management, procurement of furnishings and fittings and interior design, thus providing its clients with a unique "all in one" approach to handling their assets. Being a service provider but also acting as an investor, H&H approaches all of its projects with a critical eye, aiming to maximize efficiency and to create value for investors throughout each project’s life cycle.

name: Expo City
description: Expo City Dubai will ensure the far-reaching legacy of Expo 2020 continues to evolve and flourish for generations to come. This clean, tech-enabled city will propel human progress by harnessing the power of ‘we’.   Expo City Dubai is based on a deep-rooted belief that a broad coalition of people, working together, can propel human progress to help create a more sustainable and dignified future for all. This vision aligns with the UAE’s wider sustainability, diversification and growth goals. Driven by innovation, Expo City Dubai’s business ecosystem will bring together global talents to embrace technology and digital advances.

name: Meteora
description: A Meteora home is your ticket to elevated living. Everything around you meets the highest standards; for it has been conceived, designed and personalised with precision, passion and your dreams in mind.Meteora Developers creates premium residential developments that combine high-quality design with vibrant, modern living spaces for a diverse resident base. A combination of visionary thinking, access to top-tier debt and equity capital sources, deep development expertise, and a horizontally integrated operational network has positioned Meteora Developers as one of the most active, capable, and well-capitalized development team in the United Arab Emirates.

name: Zimaya Properties
description: Our mission is to create living environments that enrich lives and bring daily fulﬁlment, empowering individuals as they pursue their dreams and ambitions.Zimaya Properties brings together seasoned industry professionals boasting over threedecades of construction and development expertise across the UAE and India. Zimaya’s townhouse communities in Dubai have garnered widespread acclaim for its unparalleled quality, meticulous attention to detail, and exceptional layouts, commanding impressive gains for investors upon completion.

name: Tiger Group
description:
Tiger Group is one of the UAE's most established real estate developers, founded in 1976 with a vision to contribute to the country's rapid development. Over the years, the company has diversified its portfolio beyond real estate, expanding into sectors such as facilities management, hospitality, education, and healthcare. With over 45 years of experience and a track record of 270 completed projects, Tiger Group has become a trusted name in delivering high-quality developments that blend modernity with luxury​.

The company is renowned for its ambitious projects, including high-rise residential towers, commercial properties, and mixed-use developments. Tiger Group emphasizes innovation and customer satisfaction by integrating advanced technologies and sustainable practices in its construction processes. Their developments, such as Nobles Tower and Guzel Towers, reflect a commitment to creating world-class lifestyles while maintaining affordability and accessibility for a diverse clientele​.

name: Elysian Development
description: Elysian Developments is a boutique luxury real estate developer based in Dubai, conceived by the visionaries at Elysian Group — a company with a strong legacy in the Dubai property market since 2006. Guided by a philosophy that every detail matters, Elysian is committed to delivering residential environments where true excellence lies in the precision of design and the seamless blend of luxury and well-being.With a multidisciplinary team, Elysian creates thoughtfully crafted destinations that support multidimensional wellness and a deep sense of belonging. Their approach to development integrates innovative design, natural balance, and bespoke comfort to deliver spaces that promote vitality, serenity, and community living. Elysian’s vision is to redefine luxury real estate in Dubai by making it synonymous with holistic well-being. Every project is designed as a unique expression of elegance and functionality, aimed at elevating daily life through timeless architecture and a refined living experience.

name: AMWAJ Development
description: AMWAJ Development is a leading real estate developer in Dubai, pursuing its mission to provide innovative and environmentally friendly development solutions. With a focus on excellence and quality, AMWAJ Development strives to enhance the quality of life for both residents and visitors while making a positive contribution to the local community.AMWAJ Development is backed by an experienced founder and leadership team with over 25 years of diverse international experience, including 11 years specifically dedicated to property development in Europe and the Middle East. AMWAJ Development specializes in the development and sale of residential and commercial projects, aiming to create modern, premium, family-oriented living spaces in Dubai's most sought-after areas.Our mission is to reimagine Dubai's real estate environment by delivering innovative and sustainable development solutions that set new standards for the quality of urban living. We are committed to creating iconic landmarks that offer luxurious, contemporary living spaces with high-quality finishes and the integration of smart technology. Through our developments, we strive to create a cosmopolitan community that thrives on community spirit and environmental friendliness, contributing to the economic and social development of the region.We aim to lead the way in creating vibrant spaces that enhance living standards and offer diversity, redefining urban living in Dubai and beyond.Our core values drive us to undertake projects that reflect our commitment to quality and the well-being of society.

name: Mered
description: At MERED, they believe that buildings are not just glass and concrete structures, but timeless landmarks that change lives. They strive to be masters of incredible lifestyles that enrich and prosper their clients while remaining relevant for today and tomorrow.

name: Manam RED
description: Founded in 2024, Manam Real Estate Development LLC is a leader in the UAE’s real estate market, recognized for its focus on luxury and functionality in design. With a foundation built on extensive market knowledge and 30 years of residential and commercial project development experience in Oman, we are committed to bringing client visions to life with sophisticated, high-end designs that prioritize both aesthetics and practicality. Our promoters also bring 10 years of expertise in logistics hubs development in Dubai, further enhancing our capabilities. Known for our credibility and professionalism, Manam emphasizes customer satisfaction and quality, continuously striving to deliver projects that blend comfort, elegance, and innovative functionality.

name: East & West Properties
description: Welcome to East and West Properties (EWP), a distinguished developer at the forefront of luxury real estate across the UAE and beyond. Established in 1993, EWP has become synonymous with opulence and refined living, offering a discreet haven for those with an eye for excellence.Our journey as a developer began with a commitment to unmatched quality, as evidenced in our meticulously crafted exquisite villas. Over the years, we’ve evolved alongside the dynamic real estate landscape of the UAE, blending luxury with innovative design to meet and exceed the expectations of the global market.Our team of seasoned professionals expertly navigates the complexities of diverse development projects, delivering efficiency and exceptional results on time. We are steadfast in our dedication to sustainability, integrating eco-conscious practices into our developments, setting a standard for a greener future in real estate.EWP is more than a real estate entity; it is a gateway to exploring some of the most prestigious development projects in the UAE and internationally. Tailored for the astute investor and discerning individuals, our portfolio is a testament to our commitment to luxury and innovative design. Join us in this remarkable journey, where we continue to redefine excellence in every endeavor.

name: Meteora Developers
description: Meteora builds homes for those who appreciate excellence and superior craftsmanship. Their developments represent the true definition of quality with refined finishes, thoughtful floor plans and elevated amenities. The philosophy of perfection elevates and distinguishes every Meteora development. This passion originates from the founders and their belief that the home owner’s choice should extend beyond the tangibles to include views, flexible floor plans, and unrivaled amenities. The sites and locations are optimal. The materials and finishes are hand selected and sourced from around the world to deliver the finest product. The floor plans are intelligently planned to maximize light, views, and functionality. From the distinctive glass and brick facade, to the custom fixtures, hardware, stone, metals and fabrication work, to the welcoming arrivals, Meteora properties are built to be appreciated for a lifetime.

name: Ahmadyar Real Estate Development
description: Ahmadyar Developments is a beacon of upscale lifestyle & innovation in the dynamic real estate development landscape. With roots tracing back to Ahmadyar Group's inception in 1992, this esteemed entity has paved the way into a distinguished company, extending its reach across Afghanistan. the UAE, Turkey, and Europe. Specializing in premium properties and communities, Ahmadyar Developments epitomizes sophistication and excellence, catering to the discerning tastes of modern clientele. Through a strategic focus on bespoke projects tailored to contemporary lifestyles, coupled with a commitment to delivering exceptional returns investment. Ahmadyar Developments redefines quality living in Dubai and beyond.

name: Fakhruddin Properties Development
description:
Fakhruddin Properties, established in 2003, has become a prominent name in the real estate industry, offering comprehensive property development, management, and brokerage services. With a diverse portfolio of residential, commercial, and mixed-use projects, the company has expanded its footprint across key markets in the UAE, the UK, and Uganda. Their developments are strategically located to provide maximum convenience and value to investors and residents, with a focus on creating vibrant, sustainable communities.

What sets Fakhruddin Properties apart is their commitment to quality, innovation, and customer-centricity. Each project is meticulously designed, blending modern architecture with functionality and aesthetic appeal. The company integrates eco-friendly solutions, smart home technologies, and energy-efficient systems, reflecting its dedication to sustainability and environmental stewardship.

Over the years, Fakhruddin Properties has earned a reputation for delivering projects on time and maintaining the highest standards of construction and customer service. Their holistic approach ensures long-term value for stakeholders, making them a trusted partner for both local and international investors seeking profitable real estate opportunities.

name: Laraix
description: With a strong foundation since 2016, Laraix Group has built a proven track record of quality, innovation, and trust across multiple industries. Our commitment to excellence and ethical business practices has earned us a reputation as a reliable and forward-thinking organization. Leveraging decades of industry expertise and a strong family legacy, Laraix Developers marks our strategic entry into the UAE’s dynamic real estate market. Our vision is to redefine modern homeownership in Dubai by creating elegant, luxurious properties that seamlessly blend timeless design with smart pricing.

name: Barco Developers
description: Barco is a UAE-based real estate developer and part of Badami Holding Group, a diversified business group with 50 years of operations in the UAE and international markets. Founded by experienced operators with a background in real estate, finance, consulting, F&B, and manufacturing, Barco brings a disciplined, process-driven approach to residential development. The team's cross-sector expertise and track record across the UAE, Europe, and North America underpin a model built on delivery and long-term accountability.

name: The First Group
description: Over the past two decades, we have forged a reputation as one of the hospitality industry’s leading innovators, providing groundbreaking investment opportunities to clients and partners and exceptional, memorable experiences to hotel and leisure guests.Today, our high-value hospitality asset portfolio spans unique lifestyle hotel brands, exciting F&B outlets and highly popular leisure venues. Our visionary, trailblazing approach to hotel and hospitality asset management has made us a trusted partner of some of the industry’s leading global brands, including Wyndham Hotel Group, Jumeirah Hotels & Resorts, Emirates Skywards, Mont Blanc and BMW, as well as individual investors from more than 146 countries worldwide.

name: Forum Real Estate Development
description:
Forum Real Estate Development, an international developer
acclaimed for its end-to-end real estate development cycle, has
been pioneering in Dubai's market since 2015. The company not
only focuses on enhancing the quality and consumer appeal of its
properties but also acts as an investor in a variety of overseas
development projects across Europe and Asia. With a steadfast
commitment to elevating residents' quality of life, Forum Real
Estate Development employs meticulous attention to detail and
the latest technologies and materials. This approach ensures the
creation of superior living spaces that embody the principles of
Human-oriented development, setting new benchmarks for
comfort and quality in the industry.

name: MIRA Developments
description: The UAE realty market offers a unique combination of a tax-free environment, relatively low square meter prices and high rental yields. And thanks to a strong expatriate influx driving the demand for quality housing, the average annual property price growth is about 10-12%. With strong location choices and world-class quality of finishings, Mira Developments brings this investment concept to a whole new level.

name: Valores Property Development
description: Valores Development is a real estate development company founded by seasoned visionaries with over three decades of expertise in the industry. Their passion lies in creating sustainable, community-focused spaces that enhance the lifestyle of residents.Inspired by nature, Valores believes in translating the timeless lessons of harmony, balance, and beauty into their developments. Their mission is to build livable, luxurious, and sustainable communities that integrate the tranquility of nature with modern living comforts.Their vision is to be recognized regionally and beyond for creating high-end, community-centric spaces that harmonize with nature and enrich the lives of residents. Valores aims to set new standards in premium living, elevate the quality of life for residents, and enhance every neighborhood they touch through their developments.The founders of Valores emphasize a deep connection to nature, integrity, and a relentless pursuit of excellence in all aspects of their work. Their dedication to shaping lifestyles and communities that bring value to everyone is at the core of their development philosophy.

name: BnW Developments
description: BnW Developments specializes in premier real estate development, transforming visionary concepts into luxurious realities. Beyond real estate, BnW Developments excels in diverse investments, project and capital management, and forging strategic alliances, ensuring comprehensive androbust growth for its partners.

name: Citi Developers
description: With a legacy of over a decade, we proudly stand as a world-leading master developer, renowned for reshaping cityscapes and enriching communities across continents.At Citi, trust is our foundation, and experience, our currency. We understand how our residents and investors think, and we apply this knowledge in everything we do. We know that trust takes time, resources, and years to build, and we are proud to have earned and perfected it over the past decade. Join us on this journey of trust, innovation, and exceptional living experiences as we reinvent real estate landscapes across cities.

name: Brighton Holdings
description: Brighton Holdings Ltd is a real estate development company operating in Dubai, specializing in property and construction. The company is known for its residential and commercial projects, offering high-quality properties that meet international standards.Developer's projects:Oasis Tower 1

name: HMB Homes Real Estate Development
description: HMB Homes is a boutique real estate developer based in the UAE, renowned for crafting luxurious living spaces since 2014. Committed to the highest standards of quality and comfort, HMB Homes goes beyond aesthetics to create homes that are both visually stunning and highly functional. Whether delivering custom-crafted residences or designing exceptional developments, the company leverages its expertise to bring visionary concepts to life. HMB Homes envisions becoming a world-class boutique developer, celebrated for creating exquisite, high-quality living spaces tailored to the most discerning standards. Its ultimate aspiration is to be the premier choice for luxury real estate in the UAE. With a mission to design and build exceptional homes, HMB Homes strives to exceed customer expectations by combining beauty, quality, and comfort. Through unwavering dedication to its core values, the company aims to establish itself as the leading boutique real estate developer in the region.

name: Reportage Properties
description: Reportage Properties is one of the largest private developers in the United Arab Emirates, with projects in Abu Dhabi, Dubai, and now Egypt.Known for our excellence, at Reportage offer affordable, modern design homes in Abu Dhabi & Dubai for people to enjoy the lifestyle they desire. They are focused and consistent in their objective to provide innovative, modern, and affordable housing solutions that not only offer their investors an outstanding value but also provide the home buyers a safe place to live in. They build homes with unparalleled elegance and comfort that redefine experiences.

name: Acube Developers
description: As a customer-focused real estate developer, Acube is poised to revolutionize the property market in Dubai through strategic partnerships with leading businesses in the UAE. Our comprehensive real estate development solutions aim to enhance the quality of life and change mindsets. With an in-depth understanding of what both homeowners and investors need, we offer a diverse portfolio of large and small projects across Dubai.Acube is rapidly evolving into a highly sought-after entity, offering innovative and cutting-edge solutions. Our connections to top-notch investors and vendors have made us leaders in both architecture and engineering. Whether you are a homeowner or an investor, Acube is your trusted partner for all your real estate development needs.

name: JHK Heights Development
description:
JHK Heights Development is a boutique real estate company dedicated to delivering mid-rise residential communities that prioritize wellness, connectivity, and long-term value. Since 2019, the company has established a reputation for combining premium finishes and lifestyle-driven amenities with accessible pricing. With four signature developments across key Dubai neighborhoods — Warsan 4 and Liwan 2 — JHK Heights stands out for its commitment to thoughtful design, quality execution, and on-time delivery, setting a high standard in the mid-market segment.




Driven by a clear mission to create vibrant, livable spaces and a vision to become Dubai’s most trusted boutique developer by 2030, JHK Heights consistently integrates timeless design, smart functionality, and a strong sense of community into every project. Whether for young professionals, families, or investors, the company’s developments are crafted to offer more than just homes — they create belonging, value, and enduring urban lifestyles shaped by innovation, quality, and care.

name: City View Development
description: City View Developments is an outstanding real estate development company with many years of experience in the residential, commercial and hotel sectors.Headquartered in the UAE and with significant operations in Turkey and Georgia, the company has a global presence covering about 5 million square feet of residential and 1 million square feet of commercial development.City View Developments successfully cooperates with leading hotel brands such as Ennismore, offering exclusive branded residences.City View Developments sets a new standard for luxury living with carefully designed apartment buildings that combine modern design and unsurpassed comfort.

name: Grovy Real Estate Development
description: Grovy is a trusted real estate developer committed to delivering quality, value, and customer-centric experiences. Grovy Developers, established in the UAE, has been at the forefront of the real estate industry, recognized for crafting projects that blend luxury, functionality, and modern design. Since our inception, we have dedicated ourselves to creating exceptional developments that set new benchmarks for quality, innovation, and sustainability in the UAE real estate market.With over a decade of experience, Grovy Developers has consistently delivered landmark residential projects, including Alcove, Aria, and Aura. Each of these developments reflects our commitment to offering a premium living experience, robust investment potential, and long-term value.

name: Dubai Properties
description: Dubai Properties made a significant impact in 2016 by delivering over 3,000 residential units, with 2,900 of these located in the fast-growing Dubailand area, and 124 units nestled in the upscale Dubai Wharf. Each project reflects the developer's commitment to quality and the enhancement of urban living experiences.In a groundbreaking move, Dubai Properties introduced their innovative water homes at Marasi Business Bay in September 2017, with the first collection of these luxurious floating residences arriving all the way from Finland. This milestone highlights the developer’s dedication to bringing unique living concepts to Dubai's vibrant real estate market.Further expanding its portfolio, Dubai Properties also launched Riverside, a stunning 420-unit residential tower along the picturesque Dubai Water Canal. As the first of four planned Marasi towers, Riverside marks the beginning of an exciting new chapter in Business Bay, redefining waterfront living in the heart of the city.

name: Nabni
description: We are NABNI, a boutique real estate developer, where visionary design converges with unwavering integrity, innovation, and meticulous attention to detail. We reshape the luxury real estate experience by crafting living spaces that not only redefine standards but also resonate with the essence of customer-centric excellence.

name: Madar Developments
description: A design and development arm of the construction powerhouse - Al Madar Engineering.  Madar Developments exemplifies the unwavering dedication to quality and innovation synonymous with the legacy brand of Al Madar.  At Madar Developments, our mission is to create properties that defy conventions, delivering enduring value and genuine happiness to our clients. Join us as we reshape the future of property development, one exceptional project at a time.

name: Al Ali Property Investment
description: Al Ali Property Investment (API) is a trusted developer in the UAE. The company constructs residential and commercial properties, creating modern urban communities. Each project stands out with high-quality construction, thoughtful architecture, and a comfortable living environment.API focuses on providing homes that meet the needs of contemporary lifestyles. The developments feature quality materials and functional layouts. Every property is designed with essential amenities to enhance everyday comfort.The company selects promising locations, ensuring convenient access to key city landmarks. API has built a strong reputation by delivering modern residential neighborhoods and providing comfortable living conditions.

name: Amirah Developments
description: Amirah Development is a newly established property development company based in Dubai, dedicated to redefining the city’s skyline with our visionary approach to real estate. Founded by Muhammad Yousuf Jafrani, a seasoned entrepreneur with over 15 years of experience in the UAE, Amirah Development brings a fresh perspective to the property market. Our commitment to quality, innovation, and excellence drives us to create exceptional living spaces that blend luxury, comfort, and sustainability.

name: Arabian Gulf Properties
description: Arabian Gulf Properties is a distinguished real estate developer in the United Arab Emirates, renowned for its commitment to excellence and innovation in the construction and real estate sectors. Established in 1978, the company has evolved into a top-tier luxury real estate developer in the Middle East, setting high standards in the UAE's construction industry.Arabian Gulf Properties stands out for its strong associations with top-ranking public and private sector institutions, its implementation of effective quality management systems, and its adherence to environmental protection policies. By focusing on customer satisfaction, innovative design, and community-centric development, Arabian Gulf Properties continues to shape Dubai's skyline and contribute significantly to the emirate's real estate landscape.

name: STAMN Real Estate Development
description:
STAMN Real Estate Development is a distinguished subsidiary of New Bay Holdings, a prominent conglomerate with over 30 years of expertise in comprehensive development. Based in Nanchang, Jiangxi, China, the company specializes in diverse sectors, including cultural tourism, commercial and real estate development, asset management, and property services. STAMN is driven by the mission of "lighting up the city's prosperity and creating a better life for people," shaping urban landscapes through innovative and people-centric real estate projects. From commercial complexes to high-end smart residential developments, STAMN combines market expertise and professional experience to deliver superior housing options tailored to customer needs and investment solutions that ensure value growth.

In addition to real estate development, STAMN provides a broad spectrum of services, including property sales, leasing, and business operations. They offer personalized home-buying solutions, professional consulting, and rental services designed to enhance client experiences, whether for tenants or property investors. Moreover, the company is committed to building its own commercial brands and fostering regional development across Dubai and the Middle East. Their portfolio also extends to immigration and study-abroad consultancy, ensuring clients receive seamless support for relocation, living arrangements, and high-quality real estate services in new destinations. Through a focus on innovation, quality, and community enhancement, STAMN continues to redefine urban living and investment opportunities.

name: Pearlshire Developments
description:
Pearlshire Developments stands as a visionary real estate developer committed to delivering excellence and innovation in the property market. With a focus on high-quality, value-added investments, the company strategically develops projects that elevate urban living and generate above-market returns for stakeholders. Driven by meticulous due diligence and a growth-oriented mindset, Pearlshire’s real estate portfolio emphasizes lasting value, blending design excellence with enriching experiences for its residents and investors alike.

Collaboration and innovation are at the core of Pearlshire’s operations. The company partners with leading architects, contractors, and service providers to create world-class developments that push the boundaries of modern living. With a commitment to integrity, efficiency, and quality, Pearlshire continues to set benchmarks in the real estate sector, achieving the highest standards of performance and creating enduring legacies in every project it undertakes.

name: S and S
description: S&S Developments is a boutique property development firm based in Dubai, established by industry veterans with a proven track record. The company is dedicated to creating exceptional real estate projects that redefine luxury living. Their mission is to deliver intricately crafted, future-focused residential buildings and townhouses that elevate urban living standards. S&S Developments emphasizes visionary innovation, investing in human-centric research to push design boundaries and enhance the cityscape with meticulous attention to detail. Their portfolio includes notable projects such as The White Palace in Dubai Silicon Oasis, Emtilak Townhouses in Al Furjan, The Carla in Meydan Avenue, and Rise Residences in Jumeirah Village Circle. Through these developments, S&S Developments showcases its commitment to excellence, sustainability, and creating empowering living spaces that seamlessly integrate with the environment.

name: Muraba Properties
description: Muraba Properties is a boutique development company based in Dubai, specializing in creating unique residential projects with a focus on minimalism, architectural excellence, and harmony with the surrounding environment. The company collaborates with world-renowned architects, including Pritzker Prize winners, to create aesthetically pure and functional living spaces.Key projects by the developer include: Muraba Dia, Muraba Veil Muraba Properties embodies the philosophy of quiet luxury, creating projects where architecture, nature, and comfort merge into a seamless whole.

name: ARIB Developments
description: ARIB Real Estate Development Company stands at the forefront of property innovation, offering luxury living experiences framed by breathtaking cityscapes. Our extensive expertise in the industry ensures each development exemplifies sophistication, comfort, and easy access to urban amenities.

name: City View
description: City View Developments is a distinguished real estate development company boasting over decades of expertise in the residential, commercial, and hospitality sectors. Headquartered in the UAE, with significant operations in Turkey and Georgia, the company has a global footprint spanning approximately 5 million sqft of residential and 1 million sqft of commercial developments. City View Developments sets a new standard of luxury living with meticulously designed residential homes that blend contemporary design and unparalleled comfort. Their commercial properties redefine modern workspaces, offering flexible and innovative solutions to inspire creativity and productivity for businesses of all sizes. In the hospitality sector, City View Developments partners with world-renowned brands like Hyde to offer branded residences that combine residential comfort with hotel-style services, delivering an unmatched experience of luxury and hospitality.

name: Bonyan International Investment Group
description: Bonyan Group has been a pioneering force in developing the lucrative real estate market in the Gulf and MENA regions. Since entering the real estate market in 2002, which ultimately lead to the successful creation of Bonyan International Investment Group (Holding), the Company, along with its partners, co-founders and subsidiaries, has been successfully and steadily growing and developing, acquiring a prestigious reputation in the region and establishing offices in the United Arab Emirates, in Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, Al Ain, Ras Al Khaimah, Jordan, Qatar, Oman, the British Virgin Islands, the Bahamas, the Cayman Islands and many other countries. Our success is attributed to providing professional support through our staff, along with the support received by Bonyan Group and its customers. Whether taking on total ownership of a development project, or acting as partners, we offer well-established trusted expertise in every conceivable area including master planning for start-ups. Just as the name of the UAE has become synonymous with trade and enterprise all over the world, the name of the Al Habtoor Group has become synonymous with dynamic growth, evidenced by its commitment to develop and grow businesses in multiple sectors.It proudly waves the United Arab Emirates flag in many cities around the globe including London, Vienna, Budapest, Beirut and Springfield, Illinois.The Group’s hospitality division includes 14 world-class hotels; seven locally and seven abroad. The portfolio includes:Dubai, United Arab EmiratesHabtoor Grand ResortWaldorf Astoria Dubai Palm JumeirahHabtoor Palace, LXR Hotels & ResortsV Hotel, Curio Collection by HiltonHilton Dubai Al Habtoor CityMetropolitan Hotel DubaiAl Habtoor Polo ResortOverseasImperial Hotel, a Luxury Collection Hotel, Vienna (Austria)Hilton London Wembley (United Kingdom)Hilton Beirut Habtoor Grand (Lebanon)Hilton Beirut Metropolitan Palace (Lebanon)President Abraham Lincoln Springfield – a DoubleTree by Hilton Hotel (United States)InterContinental Budapest (Hungary)The Ritz-Carlton, Budapest (Hungary)Al Habtoor Motors' brand portfolio includes Mitsubishi, with a wide choice of sedans, 4x4's and commercial vehicles, two well-known Chinese brands, JAC and Chery, Temsa buses as well as premium marques such as Bentley, McLaren and Bugatti.The company has a well-established network of nine showrooms, nine service centres, four body shops and ten parts centres that effectively cover the entire UAE. In 2015, Al Habtoor Motors entered the Saudi Arabian market for the first time with Mitsubishi Fuso.Al Habtoor Motors owns and operates the world’s first – and largest – iconic Bentley Motors showroom to be built in major cities around the world. The state-of-the-art showroom is located in a prime location on Sheikh Zayed Road, with built-up area of 76,000 square feet. It consists of three basement floors designated for parking, in addition to three floors of customer area displaying over 70 vehicles, offices, boutiques, Mulliner lounge, a VIP Majlis and other related required services. Adding to its unique design, over 200 thousand LED lights illuminate the outer façade.Diamondlease specialises in short-term and long-term leasing of popular brands ranging from small to mid-sized saloons to pick-up trucks and buses.The Group’s real estate division includes a variety of commercial and residential properties from office space to luxury villas. Al Habtoor Real Estate provides a total value package, with an emphasis on client needs.The real estate division includes Al Habtoor City’s Residence Collection, currently under development. The upmarket lifestyle destination embodies exclusivity and style. The three residential towers comprise of deluxe apartments, lofts and penthouses, ranging from 1-7 bedrooms in a unique neighbourhood. Residents will have access to all Al Habtoor City’s amenities, which include the largest swimming pool podium in the UAE, a state-of-the-art gym, luxury spa, signature restaurants and have the added bonus of all being right on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal. In addition they can benefit from three five-star hotels right on their doorstep.The Al Habtoor Group has long been a pioneer in the field of education, it operates two well-established schools offering quality education from KG1 to Grade 13. Emirates International School – Jumeirah and Emirates International School – The Meadows are accredited IB World Schools.The Group’s publishing arm regularly produces quality publications including Al Shindagah magazine, a bilingual corporate magazine, which has been in circulation since1993.

name: Avelon Developments
description: Avelon Developments specializes in crafting design-oriented apartments that offer a unique community lifestyle in Dubai. With a focus on premium amenities and sophisticated design, the goal is to redefine urban living. Our customer-centric approach focuses on exceeding client expectations through build-time certainty and best-in-market prices while curating a quality of life for residents that considers a full spectrum of location, leisure and lifestyle.

The company blends modern architecture, sustainability and meticulous attention to detail to deliver homes and communities that stand the test of time. Specializing in high-quality, value-added investments in real estate, distressed assets, and debt-equity strategies, Pearlshire Capital Group strives to create enduring value for stakeholders.Their mission is to build a better tomorrow by elevating urban projects to enrich lives and deliver above-market returns. description: Svarn is a real estate developer based in the UAE. With a wealth of experience, we have established ourselves as leaders in the field, harnessing our expertise in real estate development and business management.

With a rich history dating back to 1951, the group has been a key player in the UAE’s real estate industry.Born out of a dedication to innovation and excellence, ADE Properties continues the group's legacy of success in property development. Under the leadership of Ahmad Mohd Al Dallal and Mahmood Mohd Al Dallal, sons of the late Mohammed Mahmood Al Dallal, the company represents a new chapter of progress and achievement in the family’s long-standing real estate heritage.Guided by the wisdom and vision of the late Mohammed Mahmood Al Dallal, a respected advisor and property owner, ADE Properties carries forward a strong tradition of excellence and forward-thinking in the UAE’s real estate landscape.

name: Sankari Property

As of the current time, several ambitious projects are under construction, and almost all the areas in them have already been bought up by investors from different parts of the globe.

Arista infuses each project with a unique vision, in-depth detail with contemporary values; by blending functional living spaces with quality, precision and innovative luxury.

Every luxury development delivered by Palma Holding has contributed to redefining the Dubai skyline through its uniqueness and quality. The company remains committed to providing investors and owners with upscale homes and strong investment returns for years to come.

Their journey is founded on a fundamental insight: many properties of the past were created with a sole focus on stock provision, often at the expense of quality. This short-sighted approach has significantly impacted property capital appreciation and the return on investment (ROl) over time.

Whether you are looking for a place to create your ideal home or just a good investment opportunity, AQUA Properties is a full-service real estate company providing clients personalized and valuable up-to-date market data and trends.

Palladium Prime Real Estate Development is a forward-thinking real estate developer rooted in a legacy of architectural excellence and innovation. Founded by Yusuf Al Mulla, whose family has played a significant role in shaping Dubai's urban landscape, the company draws on decades of experience and a deep understanding of the region's architectural and engineering heritage. Guided by design expertise from Wissam J. Salameh, a seasoned leader in architectural and project management, Palladium Prime Real Estate Development combines innovative design with meticulous attention to detail. The company is committed to creating unique and functional spaces that enhance the lives of residents while contributing to the growth and modernization of Dubai’s real estate sector. Through its dedication to quality, sustainability, and customer satisfaction, Palladium Prime Real Estate Development sets a high benchmark for excellence in the industry.

name: Reef Luxury Development
description:
As a visionary developer in Dubai, Reef Developments is dedicated to transforming living with innovative and practical solutions. Their commitment to provide exceptional value quality and meticulous attention to detail ensures timely delivery and elevates the real estate experience to new heights.

They are motivated by their commitment to creating a legacy of pioneering luxury living in Dubai, reshaping the future of real estate through innovation, value and ambition. They bring over 10 years of experience in real estate development. They have collaborated with prominent developers and successfully completed numerous high-profile projects which demonstrate their expertise and commitment to excellence in the industry.

name: DarGlobal

We profoundly believe in the timeless value of luxury, a kind of wealth in constant growth for its own intrinsic nature, that represents one of the wisest and most foresighted investments of our changing times. Established in 2017 to upend the global luxury real estate market, Dareglobal combines experience and innovation to deliver the highest quality properties.World-class architects curate DarGlobal’s homes, which are modeled by renowned design and fashion icons; each home is built with the highest quality materials and maintained by top experts within the field. Dareglobal is always the first to scout the most prestigious and attractive locations, providing lucrative investment opportunities for a distinct clientele.

name: Meydan
description: Meydan is the visionary concept of His Highness Sheikh Mohammed Bin Rashid Al Maktoum, UAE Vice President, Prime Minister and Ruler of Dubai. The project is the culmination of his vision to create not just a venue for horseracing, but an integrated city that is sustainable. Meydan group, through its various projects, provides individuals and families elegant lifestyle opportunities and access to top entertainment and sporting events.

name: API
description: Community is the cornerstone of life; it’s the foundation of happiness, success and prosperity. At API, this mindset is at the very heart of everything they do - and has been from day one. Since 1985, they’ve been creating environments that give birth to flourishing communities; places where people thrive and where businesses prosper. But this takes more than just bricks and mortar, and it takes more than just a landlord. It’s about putting people first, thinking about the small details that make big differences. It’s about being a partner to depend upon for life’s daily challenges, however great or small. Perhaps more than anything else, it’s about saying what we’ll do and doing what they say, so you can simply focus on you. They exist to create communities that fulfil potential. Whether you’re a potential resident, partner or even employee, let API help you live your best life.

name: Al Tareq Star Real Estate Development
description: Al-Tareq Star is a visionary real estate developer led by Sheikh Tariq Ali al-Tamimi, whose decades of experience and strong cultural roots drive the company’s mission. Focused on creating meaningful, high-quality communities, the firm blends heritage with modern design across projects in Saudi Arabia and Dubai. With a legacy built on trust, craftsmanship, and smart planning, Al-Tareq Star delivers enduring value and livability through purposefully designed spaces that foster connection and comfort.

name: Saba Properties
description:
For more than 20 years, SABA Properties has built a distinguished reputation as a reliable and esteemed property developer in Dubai. The company is known for its unwavering commitment to quality and high standards. Particularly, the SABA Towers in JLT exemplify their dedication to excellence, consistently upholding remarkably high property values in the market.

Founded in 2003, SABA Properties has been a leader in property development in Dubai, focusing primarily on Jumeirah Lakes Towers (JLT). Their journey began with the ambition to leverage the newly introduced Freehold Law in Dubai, leading to numerous significant achievements.

SABA Properties proudly completed three impressive 40-story towers in the heart of JLT, including SABA-1, a commercial landmark, and SABA-2 & SABA-3, elegant residential projects. Together, these towers offer over nine hundred units, setting a new standard for luxury living.

In 2003, SABA Properties introduced the first freehold office tower in Dubai and followed with the first handover in the Jumeirah Lakes Towers district in 2006. Additionally, SABA Properties manages and maintains its own buildings through its subsidiary, SABA Property Management, ensuring that the properties are upheld to the highest standards to preserve their value over time.

name: MVS Real Estate Development
description: MVS Real Estate Development is an international development company and part of the MAVIS Group, with over 18 years of industry experience. Headquartered in Dubai’s Opal Tower, the company is known for delivering high-quality residential and commercial real estate projects across multiple countries, including the UAE, UK, and Russia. To date, MVS has completed more than 42 residential complexes, comprising over 22,000 apartments and covering a total area of around 1.2 million square meters. The company has also developed significant commercial spaces—including hypermarkets, warehouses, and shopping centers — exceeding 56,000 square meters in total. MVS is recognized for its exclusive architectural designs, thoughtful layouts, cutting-edge engineering solutions, and carefully curated landscaping. It places special emphasis on infrastructure, integrating playgrounds, sports areas, promenades, and relaxation zones into its projects.

name: Empire Developments
description: Embark on a journey of luxury and refinement as you elevate your lifestyle to unparalleled heights at Empire Developments. Our commitment to excellence ensures an extraordinary living experience, where opulence meets innovation. Welcome to a realm where every moment, every detail, and every space transcends the ordinary, offering a lifestyle beyond compareDiscover a world where every detail is a work of art and every corner is a testament to precision. At Empire Developments, we redefine living with spaces that are meticulously crafted to offer an unparalleled experience of sophistication and comfort. Welcome to a life where every aspect of your home reflects the dedication to craftsmanship and the pursuit of perfection.

name: Tabeer
description: In the fast-paced, cosmopolitan city of Dubai, the real estate market is as dynamic as the skyline. Here, luxury and innovation are the norms, not the exception. Against this vibrant backdrop, Tabeer Real Estate Development has been making its mark since its establishment in 2014, In the fast-paced, cosmopolitan city of Dubai, the real estate market is as dynamic as the skyline. Here, luxury and innovation are the norms, not the exception. Against this vibrant backdrop, Tabeer Real Estate Development has been making its mark since its establishment in 2014 stands as a leading property developer in Dubai, specializing in crafting high-quality, affordable residential spaces. Beginning our journey in the thriving district of International City, we’ve set new benchmarks for superior living experiences for both local and expatriate residents.

name: Stamn Development
description: About STAMNSTAMN Real Estate Development is an independent overseas subsidiary of New Bay Holdings, a group company headquartered in Nanchang, Jiangxi, China, with 30 years of comprehensive development experience; The group company was established in 1993.

name: Sankari Properties
description: Sankari Properties, established in 2023, is the real estate division of the Sankari Investment Group, a company with a 40-year legacy in high-end fashion and retail through its flagship, Paris Group. The company is committed to redefining luxury living in Dubai by developing opulent residential projects that reflect unparalleled craftsmanship and bold design. Their inaugural project, "One Sankari," is a $1 billion twin-tower development located in the prestigious Marasi Marina area of Business Bay. Scheduled for completion in the fourth quarter of 2027, this development offers exclusive three, four, and five-bedroom apartments, each occupying an entire floor to ensure maximum privacy and security. Amenities include private pools in each residence, spa facilities, a wine vault, cigar rooms, a golf simulator, and indoor swimming pools. Under the leadership of Chairman Mohammed Sankari and CEO Mark Phoenix, Sankari Properties aims to elevate Dubai's real estate landscape by creating spaces that transcend traditional luxury, embodying personal expression and innovative design.

name: Siadah Development
description: A commitment to promoting a healthier environment and developing sustainable, high-living standard communities for emerging and future generations. Newly established in early 2018, SIADAH is a Real Estate Development company founded by subject matter experts.

name: Taraf Holding
description: Taraf is a luxury and boutique residential property developer based in Dubai, United Arab Emirates. Established in early 2023 as a subsidiary of Yas Holding, Taraf aims to deliver thoughtfully curated and exclusive residential properties in iconic and prime locations across the UAE, catering to discerning national and international clients.  In October 2023, Taraf announced a partnership with the international fashion house KARL LAGERFELD to collaborate on a luxury branded villas project in Dubai. This development marks KARL LAGERFELD's first branded residential property in the Middle East and reflects Taraf's commitment to delivering high-quality offerings in the UAE's real estate sector. As a company under Yas Holding, a leading investment group headquartered in the UAE, Taraf's launch aligns with the group's efforts to diversify its portfolio and set new standards for a luxurious lifestyle for residents and investors in the UAE and beyond.

name: Mashriq Elite Real Estate Development
description: Mashriq Group - your trusted partner in Real Estate, Project Development, and Telecommunication. With over two decades of experience, we have become pioneers in these industries, having network not only in the UAE but also across United States, Europe, Singapore, Saudi Arabia, and the wider region.Our collateral team of highly skilled professionals collaborates closely with architects, engineers, contractors, and local authorities to ensure successful project delivery, adhering to the highest standards of quality, sustainability, and safety.Our success stems from our commitment to customer satisfaction, innovation, and delivering tailored solutions. We excel in on-time, on-budget, high-quality project delivery. We adapt to industry trends, embrace technology, and thrive on overcoming challenges.Choose Al Mashriq Group as your partner to ignite possibilities, unlock potential, and elevate your projects to new heights of successIn the realm of Real Estate, we specialize in a wide range of services including property development, investment, sales, and management across the Asian and Middle-East regions. We have successfully completed a substantial count of residential and commercial segment in the region (such as Floarea projects), catering to the evolving needs of our clients.

name: SRG Holding
description: Dubai based SRG Holding is one of the leading family-owned holding companies in the UAE, with extensive operations in property development and management, hospitality, real estate investments, and wholesale trading. Founded in 1958 by Abdulsalam AlRafi to trade agricultural commodities such as tea, sugar and rice in the AlRas Deira souq, SRG Holding has since grown to become one of the Emirate’s leading family-owned holding companies, with extensive operations. Some of the city’s most recognisable landmarks have been built and managed by SRG Holding, including Burj Al Salam, Sheraton Grand Hotel Dubai, AlSalam Hotel Suites, Marina Heights Tower and AlSalam Grand Hotel & Hotel Apartments. The group operates across the entire real estate value chain, including project development, facilities management, and leasing and sales services.

name: Yard
description:
Yard - the first real estate developer in Dubai, specializing in creating recharge properties. Given the shortage of green areas in Dubai, Yard's philosophy revolves around blending nature with the urban environment. The name of the yard real estate developer not only associates with a garden but also symbolizes a unit of space measurement in Dubai. CG Investment LTD is a top development and construction company in Montenegro that has set a new level for real estate in the region, thereby attracting large investments in this area. 

The group of investors in partnership with CG Investment LTD set itself the goal to bring a unique natural atmosphere to the Middle East, establishing here the development company One Yard Real Estate LLC. 

The company’s aim is to bring a European approach to the UAE market.

name: Topero Properties
description: Topero Properties, a prominent property development company in UAE, is revolutioning the industry with a strategic vision. Topero ́s new brand balance Emirati cultural identity and a modern outlook, appealing to the majority of young Emiratis and expats, who seek stylish, modern, sophisticated and relevant brands that resonate with their values.

AMWAJ Development, backed by seasoned founder and leadership team that bring over 25 years of diverse international experience, including 11 years specifically dedicated to real estate development across Europe and the Middle East. AMWAJ Development is focused on the construction and sale of residential and commercial projects with a commitment to deliver premium contemporary family-centric living spaces in Dubai’s most popular neighborhoods.

description: Axiom Prime Real Estate is a distinguished real estate company known for its commitment to delivering exceptional property solutions. description: R.evolution – a high-end boutique real estate developer from Europe. Across residential, office, hotel and infrastructural properties, and in cities from Riga to Barcelona and Dubai to Berlin, R.Evolution has brought a unique approach and DNA to real estate development.

With a foundation built on trust, quality, and an unwavering dedication to delivering superior results, Golden Woods Real Estate Development has created a legacy that speaks for itself.Led by the CEO, the company's focus is on crafting spaces where exceptional design seamlessly merges with functionality, resulting in environments that not only inspire but also stand the test of time. Their projects are designed to surpass expectations by marrying exceptional quality with a positive and lasting impact on the communities they serve.Golden Woods Real Estate Development invites all stakeholders to join them in shaping the future, with a collective effort towards creating developments that inspire, endure, and drive mutual success.

The company's projects are located in some of the most desirable areas in Dubai, including Jumeirah Lake Towers (JLT).Me Do Re Properties is committed to creating high-quality developments that meet the needs of its customers. The company's projects are designed to be energy-efficient and to use recycled materials. Me Do Re Properties also partners with local businesses to support the local economy.

name: Ginco Properties
description: The management of GINCO PROPERTIES (GP) is based on the company's belief in providing 360° real estate management services so that clients can benefit from a holistic living experience. Under the guidance of GP management, a calm and stylish lifestyle is always guaranteed. We are pioneers in managing large-scale communities in the form of freestanding towers in Dubai and other Emirates. Our team constantly pays attention to the needs of our customers and tenants. Providing a pleasant stay has become our hallmark, resulting in long-term relationships.As one of the region's leading real estate management firms, GP understands the value of well-built managed real estate. This leads to longer lease agreements and maximization of return on investment.

name: Al Marwan Developments
description: Since its founding in 1978, Al Marwan Group has established itself as a leading provider of comprehensive services across the construction, heavy equipment, investment, hospitality, and real estate sectors. Over the decades, the group has grown into one of the most prominent and respected names in the development industry, known for its commitment to quality, innovation, and client satisfaction. Today, Al Marwan Group operates a diverse portfolio of subsidiaries involved in construction, real estate development, heavy equipment rental and sales, port management, oilfield services, and robotic solutions. As one of the region's largest and most reliable suppliers of heavy equipment, asphalt, and concrete, the group serves as a one-stop solution for the construction industry, catering to both public and private sector clients. Headquartered in the UAE, Al Marwan Group maintains a strong presence across the GCC, as well as in Canada, Africa, and the Far East. The group has earned numerous accolades, including the titles of 2023 Sharjah’s Leading Hotel, Category A Contractor (Unlimited), and 2023 Heavy Equipment Rental Company in the GCC. With a reputation built on trust and excellence, Al Marwan Group continues to support major infrastructure and development projects throughout its extensive operational footprint.

name: Amer Al Ghurair
description: Founded in 1996, Amer Al Ghurair Real Estate has built a strong reputation for expertise, integrity, and a forward-thinking approach, providing professional property services across Dubai. Specializing in property sales, leasing, and management across both residential and commercial sectors, AGRE has grown to become one of Dubai’s leading real estate firms, managing an expanding portfolio of over 1,200 properties throughout the city. Under the leadership of Chairman Mr. Amer Abdulla Al Ghurair, is committed to redefining excellence in the industry, delivering exceptional services and innovative concepts to their clients, while prioritizing the development of long-term relationships at every stage of their property journey.

name: Manam Realty
description: Founded in 2024, Manam Real Estate Development LLC is a leader in the UAE’s real estate market, recognized for its focus on luxury and functionality in design. With a foundation built on extensive market knowledge and 30 years of residential and commercial project development experience in Oman, they are committed to bringing client visions to life with sophisticated, high-end designs that prioritize both aesthetics and practicality. Their promoters also bring 10 years of expertise in logistics hubs development in Dubai, further enhancing their capabilities. Known for their credibility and professionalism, Manam emphasizes customer satisfaction and quality, continuously striving to deliver projects that blend comfort, elegance, and innovative functionality.

name: FIM Partners
description:
FIM Partners is a leading investment management firm headquartered in Dubai, specializing in frontier and emerging markets with a strong emphasis on long-term, responsible investing. Founded on a commitment to delivering value through local insight and disciplined strategy, the firm manages a diversified portfolio that spans equities, fixed income, and real estate. With offices in key financial hubs such as London, Riyadh, and Muscat, FIM Partners combines global reach with regional expertise.




As a real estate developer, FIM Partners focuses on high-quality, community-driven projects that prioritize sustainable growth and institutional standards. Their development arm is involved in transforming prime assets—such as branded residences—into thoughtfully designed, high-value investments. Their approach reflects a commitment to excellence, underpinned by strong governance, investor transparency, and a deep understanding of local markets.

The company's portfolio often includes iconic skyscrapers, upscale villas, and state-of-the-art office spaces, all characterized by their commitment to quality, sustainability, and exceptional customer service

The company specializes in creating high-quality residential and commercial properties, combining modern design, sustainable technologies, and comfortable living environments. Tarrad Development has successfully executed projects in Iraq, Turkey, and Europe, and is now actively expanding its presence in Dubai's real estate market.Since its inception, the company has focused its operations in Dubai, particularly in the Dubai Islands area, where its key projects are being developed.

We specialise in the premium segment of the real estate industry, offering homes of optimum quality in family-oriented communities that enhance the quality of life for our residents.The name ‘Symbolic’ was chosen to reflect our real estate projects’ core values and mission. ‘Symbolic’ represents the power of symbols, which convey complex ideas, emotions, and aspirations. We believe that our real estate projects should be not only physical structures but also symbols of our commitment to sustainable living, community-oriented neighbourhoods, and overall well-being.

description:
Over the past decade, GJ Properties Investments L.L.C. has solidified its reputation as one of the premier luxury real estate developers in the UAE, with a focus on delivering high-quality projects across Ajman and the Northern Emirates. With a portfolio of 15 successful projects, the company has continually prioritized creating living spaces that elevate the quality of life for their customers, distinguishing them in the competitive UAE real estate market.




GJ Properties is dedicated to exceptional craftsmanship, innovative design, and thoughtful attention to residents' needs, ensuring that each development provides a luxurious and functional environment. From contemporary interiors to well-planned layouts, every detail reflects the company’s commitment to quality and comfort. The developments offer a range of amenities that cater to modern urban lifestyles, with spaces designed for both relaxation and community engagement.




This commitment to quality and customer satisfaction has positioned GJ Properties Investments L.L.C. as a trusted name in the real estate industry. The company’s vision is centered on creating not only homes but also vibrant communities where residents can thrive.

name: Pure Gold Living

Pure Gold Living is a real estate development arm of Pure Gold Group, known for delivering luxury residential projects in key locations across the UAE. With a focus on high-quality construction and attention to detail, Pure Gold Living offers premium homes that cater to modern urban lifestyles. Their developments are designed to provide a blend of comfort, style, and convenience, appealing to discerning buyers looking for upscale living environments.

Committed to excellence, Pure Gold Living emphasizes luxury finishes, innovative design, and exceptional amenities to enhance the living experience. The company is recognized for creating elegant homes that meet the needs of its clients, whether they are looking for contemporary apartments or spacious villas. By maintaining a strong commitment to quality and customer satisfaction, Pure Gold Living has established itself as a trusted name in the competitive UAE real estate market.
