HZ Development aims to create innovative solutions and ideas in the real estate market. With a focus on sustainability and eco-friendly living environments, they strive to maximize investment returns while maintaining a strong business ethos based on integrity, ethics, and environmental commitment. Their approach emphasizes the creation of sustainable and high-quality living environments, designed to meet the evolving needs of their clients, employees, and the wider community.

name: Peak Summit Real Estate Development
description: Peak Summit Real Estate Development is a relatively new but ambitious player in Dubai’s real estate market. Founded around 2022–2023, the company has quickly positioned itself as a boutique developer focusing on premium residential properties with a distinctly European touch. Its developments are characterized by contemporary design, eco-friendly materials, and high-end amenities that cater to modern urban lifestyles. Although still young, Peak Summit is gaining recognition for combining aesthetic appeal with practicality, aiming to redefine what comfortable, community-centered living looks like in Dubai. The company’s flagship project is The Orchard Place, a multi-phase residential development located in Jumeirah Village Circle (JVC), one of Dubai’s fastest-growing neighborhoods. With a design inspired by Mediterranean and European architecture, The Orchard Place promotes not only elegant living spaces but also a vibrant, wellness-focused environment. From its first phase, which saw towers A and B fully sold out even before construction was completed, to the more recent launches of Tower C and the final Solena phase (towers D and E), the project has drawn significant investor and buyer interest. Units range from studios to spacious penthouses and townhouses, many with double-height ceilings, private terraces, and plunge pools.

name: Rijas Aces Property
description: Rijas ACES is a real estate development company of Rijas Group managed by a highly experienced team. The business provides a real estate operating platform for high quality residential, Commercial and mixed-use development opportunities. The founding directors of Rijas ACES have operated through many market cycles and have a proven track record. Rijas ACES have been involved in acquisitions of real estate on a strategic basis with a goal of realizing capital gains and income.

name: Richmind
description: Richmind is a premium real estate developer specializing in ultra-niche, luxury residential projects. As the flagship business vertical of Richmind Holding, the company is dedicated to creating living environments that transcend mere structures, blending artistry, nature, and human-centric design. Richmind's approach is characterized by meticulous attention to detail, transparency, and in-house expertise. By assembling world-class teams, they ensure excellence is woven into every stage of development. Their philosophy fosters a continuous dialogue between people, architecture, and the natural world, resulting in homes and destinations that respond intuitively to their surroundings and the needs of those who inhabit them. Richmind's global reach, with a footprint in the UK, Portugal, Spain, and other European nations, positions it as a significant player in the luxury real estate landscape. Their vision is to build a legacy that endures and inspires future generations, creating masterpieces with unique identities and personalities.

name: Mada’in Properties
description: Mada’in Properties PJSC is a UAE-based real estate development company headquartered in Dubai. Established in late 2006, the company is owned by 300 shareholders from the UAE and GCC regions, including entities such as Gulf Investment House, Awqaf & Minors Affairs Foundation, Emirates Islamic Bank, Abu Dhabi Islamic Bank, and Al Qudra Holding. The company's vision is to be a world-class boutique property developer, focusing on innovative design, superior product value, timely delivery, and meticulous standards. Their mission emphasizes creating iconic, sustainable, and community-centric real estate projects that provide value to customers, stakeholders, and society at large.The company operates with core values centered on innovation, quality, sustainability, customer-centricity, integrity, and community engagement. Their commitment to these principles is evident in their projects, which aim to redefine the UAE's real estate landscape with unique, boutique properties that surpass expectations in detail, design, and 5-star experiences.

name: Coming soon
description: Information on the developer is coming soon

name: Gulf House Real Estate Development
description: They are at the forefront of architectural innovation, redefining what luxury living means. Central to their philosophy is the belief that true luxury lies in crafting bespoke homes that mirror each client’s unique vision and aspirations. By collaborating closely with world-renowned architects and interior designers, they are transforming the landscape of high-end real estate. Their unwavering commitment to excellence is epitomized by the extraordinary Solaia Palm Jumeirah duplexes and residences — each one distinguished by unique features that elevate them far beyond conventional developments. From bold, cutting-edge architecture to breathtaking views, these properties are the embodiment of refined luxury. Yet, their vision extends beyond design mastery. They understand that exceptional living is also about unmatched service. Every detail is meticulously considered to ensure that each client's personal needs and desires are met, delivering an elevated lifestyle experience that is truly one-of-a-kind.

name: B N H Real Estate Developer
description: B.N.H Property Real Estate Development and Management is renowned for its innovative approach to urban real estate investment and management. Steered by the visionary leadership of its founder and CEO, Mr. Muhammad Nasir Muhammad Iqbal, in collaboration with Mr. Muhammad Bilal Muhammad Nasir, the firm has set benchmarks with its series of luxurious projects that have reshaped the UAE’s property market, particularly in Dubai. B.N.H's focus is on pioneering luxury projects that not only offer high returns but also significantly transform the real estate landscape, establishing new standards for luxury and innovation in the sector.

name: Laya Developers (Akshara Global)
description:
Laya Developers is a prominent real estate brand in Dubai, known for offering high-quality apartments with premium finishing at accessible prices. Rooted in the Sanskrit term “Laya,” meaning “residence,” the company blends traditional values with modern innovation to deliver exceptional living spaces. Laya Developers focuses on creating vibrant communities in some of Dubai's most sought-after locations, ensuring a seamless blend of luxury, convenience, and affordability. From studio apartments to 1- and 2-bedroom residences, their projects have consistently achieved rapid sellouts, reflecting their dedication to value and customer satisfaction. Their philosophy emphasizes personalized service, long-lasting client relationships, and reliable, trustworthy solutions for both homebuyers and investors.

Since its inception in 2014, Laya Developers has achieved remarkable milestones. Starting with the successful launch of Laya Residences, they have continued to raise the bar with projects like Laya Mansion in 2020, offering 235 thoughtfully designed homes, and Laya Heights, handed over in 2023 with luxurious amenities like an outdoor cinema. Their latest endeavor, Laya Courtyard, is set to redefine modern living with unmatched features in a thriving Dubai neighborhood. With a steadfast commitment to excellence and customer-centric solutions, Laya Developers’ journey is marked by growth, innovation, and a promise to deliver bigger and better projects in the years ahead.

name: Laraix Group
description:
Laraix Group has established itself as a trusted name across multiple industries since its inception in 2016, built on a foundation of quality, innovation, and ethical business practices. With decades of industry expertise and a strong family legacy, the company has expanded its vision into the UAE’s real estate market through Laraix Developers, aiming to redefine modern homeownership in Dubai. By blending timeless design with smart pricing, Laraix Developers is committed to delivering luxurious and elegant properties that meet the evolving needs of homeowners and investors alike.




Guided by a philosophy of innovation, sustainability, and customer-centricity, Laraix Group continuously adapts to a competitive market through its diversified business portfolio. The company prioritizes efficiency and environmental responsibility, from sustainable water production to smart real estate developments. Under the leadership of Kabir Sundoo Larai, Jay Larai, and Sagar Larai, Laraix Group remains dedicated to creating forward-thinking, high-quality developments that set new standards in Dubai’s dynamic real estate landscape.

name: IGO
description: Invest Group Overseas is a leading investment and property development company with an extensive portfolio of delivered premium properties. We are renowned for our unrivaled ability to identify and capitalize on business opportunities in developed and emerging markets, which has seen us become one of the top investment companies in the Middle East.Developer's projects:- Catch Residences - Society House - The Paragon - Azura Residences - Pelagos by IGO - The Polo Residence

name: IMKAN Properties
description:
KAN Properties is an Abu Dhabi-based real estate developer renowned for creating soulful places that enrich people's lives.  wholly-owned subsidiary of Abu Dhabi Capital Group, IMKAN has established a diverse portfolio of 26 projects spanning two continents. (kan.ae)




The company's ethos centers on a unique research-driven approach to development, enabling IMKAN to identify and cater to the specific needs and desires of various customer segments, from millennials to erning high-net-worth individuals. This commitment to understanding their clientele allows IMKAN to design and deliver communities that foster sense of belonging dell-being. (imkan.ae)




IMKAN's vision is to redefine the real estate industry by creating soulful places that enrich lives while generating value all stakeholders, including residents, partners, colleagues, and owners. The company's mission focuses on developing a diverse and unique portfoliodevelopments that cater to different market segments and opportunities. By embracing their potent heritage, leveraging strong research capabilities, and fostering an environment that nurtures growth, IMKAN strives touild integrated comnies that are enriching for generations to come. (imkan.ae)




Notable projects by IMKAN include AlJurf, a tranquil coastal retreat nestled between Abu Dhabi and Dubai; Makers District, a vibrant community on Al Reem Island designed to inire creativity; andhkha Fatima Park, Abu Dhabi's first urban park offering a unique recreational experience. (imkan.ae)




Under the leadership of Chief Executive Officer Engineer Suwaidan Al-Dhaheri, IMKAN continues tset high standards  the real estate sector, driving success and making a lasting impact through its innovative and research-based approach to development. (imkan.ae)

name: Majid Developments
description: Majid Developments has been at the forefront of the Middle East luxury real estate market since 2004. Founded by Mansoor Majid, we are on a mission to create sustainable, vibrant communities where people thrive and connect. With a legacy of over 20 years, we’ve redefined the art of real estate development.Majid Development is dedicated to creating high-quality residential communities and lifestyle attractions in Dubai, and it has an impressive portfolio that includes technologically complex and iconic residences and corporate buildings. Hence, our reputation has been developed and attained by a network of incredibly skilled and professional people working consistently hard and producing excellent results for our clients.Our commitment to quality and love for innovation has helped us rise to the top of the sector throughout the years. We have come a long way from our modest beginnings to become a reputable pioneer in sustainable development. Thus, we aim to provide you with a sustainable space that you can proudly call home.

name: Khamas Group of Investment Companies and Kappa Acca Real Estate Development
Expo City Development
description: Expo City is a Dubai-based government real estate developer that is responsible for the construction of the Dubai World Expo site. Expo City Dubai is committed to a reputable sustainable reporting framework and its principles of transparency, continuity, accuracy, materiality and balance. These principles equally characterize how they are currently embedding sustainability across Expo City Dubai. Expo City Dubai aims to create a lasting positive impact by fostering innovation, cultural exchange, and economic growth within the UAE and beyond.

name: Kappa Acca Real Estate Development
description: The developer Kappa Acca Real Estate Development is part of the Khamas Group of companies. It is a leading and respected construction company in the UAE, implementing projects in the residential and commercial real estate segments. The landmark projects of the Kappa Acca Real Estate Development company are the 14—storey The Ritz-Carlton with hotel rooms and first-class amenities for work and leisure, as well as the MAMA Residences residential complex in the Business Bay area. The latter features studios, apartments and an ultra-luxurious penthouse. When developing projects, the developer pays attention not only to the functional layout of housing, but also to the development of internal infrastructure.

name: Dia Development
description: DIA Development has emerged as a dynamic and forward-thinking force within the UAE’s luxury real estate landscape. With a refined focus on innovation, sustainability, and human-centered design, the company represents a new generation of developers who see beyond conventional structures and strive to shape meaningful, inspiring living environments. At the heart of DIA’s philosophy lies a commitment to architectural integrity and urban harmony, expressed through projects that seamlessly blend contemporary aesthetics with practical elegance. Operating out of Dubai—a city that itself symbolizes ambition and transformation—DIA Development brings together international expertise and local insight. The company’s team, composed of seasoned professionals and creative minds, collaborates across disciplines to ensure that each project reflects a distinct identity while aligning with the broader vision of urban livability. Whether crafting a residential retreat or a vibrant mixed-use community, DIA remains dedicated to creating spaces that elevate lifestyles and foster connection.

name: Grovy Developers
description:
Grovy Developers is a trusted UAE-based real estate developer known for delivering quality, value, and customer-centric experiences. With over a decade of expertise, the company has established itself at the forefront of the market by crafting residential projects that seamlessly blend luxury, functionality, and modern design. Flagship developments such as Alcove, Aria, and Aura reflect Grovy’s commitment to premium living, long-term investment value, and high standards of sustainability. By focusing on a selective number of high-impact projects, Grovy Developers ensures meticulous attention to every detail—from concept to completion.




Guided by core values of innovation, quality, integrity, and excellence, Grovy Developers takes pride in creating spaces that foster community, enhance lifestyles, and stand the test of time. Their in-house team oversees every stage of development with transparency and precision, integrating energy-efficient, eco-conscious solutions into each project without compromising on luxury. With a clear vision to become the developer of choice in the UAE, Grovy continues to shape the future of real estate by delivering homes that go beyond expectations and build lasting value for all stakeholders.

name: Vision Developments
description: Vision Developments believes in the power of architecture to transform not just landscapes, but lives. Founded by visionary leader Masoud Al Zarooni, the company is committed to innovation and sustainability, setting new standards in real estate development. Vision Developments aims to craft environments that enhance everyday living through forward-thinking design, sustainable practices, and community-oriented development. Every project is approached as an opportunity to foster harmony and elevate the human experience in urban spaces. The company’s mission is to lead the industry by creating value for clients through the development of meticulously designed, eco-friendly, and technologically advanced properties. Vision Developments strives to build sustainable communities that improve quality of life and promote long-term prosperity.

name: MAG
description:
MAG Property Development is the real estate development arm of MAG Group Holding. MAG PD is one of the largest names in the region’s real estate industry, with current project estimates at over USD 5 billion.

The company focuses on developing and delivering exceptional projects that are created with the aim of enhancing lifestyles and providing long-term benefits to both investors and customers. Their developments span from luxury high-rise residential towers and vast multi-billion dollar communities, to innovative real estate projects that feature wellness-focused lifestyles.

name: True Future Real Estate Development
description: True Future Real Estate Development Company, a Dubai, UAE-based company focused on building and villa projects. We are a leader in the real estate sector.We specialize in developing and constructing luxury construction projects, including buildings and villas, and aim to provide exceptional residential experiences for our clients.Our company stands out for its beautiful, modern designs and use of the latest technologies and innovative materials in construction. We strive to achieve the highest standards of quality and excellence in every project we undertake.Our projects include a variety of residential and commercial buildings, including luxury residential towers and modern residential complexes. We also design and build luxury villas featuring high-end details and exclusive amenities.We are committed to providing exceptional service to our customers by focusing on innovation, quality, and strong customer engagement. We ensure customer satisfaction and strive to realize their visions and meet their needs.

name: Kingdom By MAG
description:
Kingdom By MAG is a premier real estate developer and investment partner in Dubai, known for its commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction. With a focus on delivering luxurious properties and high-return investments, the company caters to discerning buyers seeking exclusive residences and lucrative opportunities in the dynamic Dubai property market.

Renowned for its expertise and personalized approach, Kingdom By MAG offers tailored solutions for clients, whether they are purchasing a dream home, exploring investment options, or expanding their property portfolios. With an in-depth understanding of the best areas to invest in Dubai, the developer ensures that every project combines architectural brilliance, premium quality, and strategic locations that define modern living.

name: Five Holdings Properties
description: Five Holdings Properties is renowned for its extraordinary locations, local employment opportunities, stunning architecture, and design. Unlike most developers who outsource the vital early stages of projects, Five Holdings Properties retains control over cost management, project oversight, site supervision, project accounting, and procurement. By keeping these key functions in-house, they eliminate inefficiencies and implement best practices.

name: Cirrera
description:
Cirrera exists to reimagine modern living through beautifully engineered spaces where intelligent design, refined aesthetics, and enduring quality come together to enhance how people live, today and for decades to come.
Through proprietary technical solutions, Cirrera can deliver up to 12% more usable internal space than comparable developments; a feat of engineering that is both felt and measured. This is space, reengineered to work harder and feel better.
Every Cirrera project starts with a blank canvas and a clear point of view: design with intelligence, build with precision, and create spaces that feel as good as they look.

name: Wahat Al Zaweya
description: Inspired by Abu Dhabi Vision 2030, Wahat Al Zaweya has adopted a policy of sustainable economy in its projects that evidently meet environmental safety standards and motivate green activities, such as home gardening

name: Iraz Developments
description: Iraz Developments, at the core of its inception, reflects the dynamic evolution of the UAE. Co-founded by Mr. Irfan Khokar and Mr. Hassan Raza, who have been instrumental in watching the UAE's market transition from a burgeoning commercial center to a global hub. Their combined experience of over 28 years in diverse businesses across the Middle East and global markets led them to capitalize on the opportunities in the flourishing UAE real estate landscape, thus giving rise to Iraz Developments.This enterprise leverages its founders' extensive knowledge and track records in business to foster growth and innovation in real estate projects. With a keen eye on modern developments and a commitment to quality, Iraz Developments aims to contribute significantly to the UAE's property sector, driven by leadership that values sustainability and forward-thinking strategies.

name: Galaxy Realty
description:
Galaxy Realty stands as a beacon of opulence and innovation in the world of luxury real estate. Since its founding in 1994 under the visionary leadership of Mr. P.M. Kunhamad, Galaxy has redefined the gold standard for premium living in South India. With an impressive legacy spanning over 1.5 million square feet in Kozhikode, the company has catered to more than 900 discerning luxury enthusiasts. Iconic developments such as Ritz Marina, Eleve Maison, Magnum Opus, and Atmosphere—the tallest residential tower in Kerala—epitomize Galaxy’s commitment to unparalleled craftsmanship, elegance, and architectural brilliance.

As Galaxy Realty celebrates three decades of excellence, the company embarks on a bold new chapter by entering the prestigious UAE real estate market. This expansion reflects their dedication to blending luxury and sophistication on a global scale. With a continued focus on creating architectural masterpieces and delivering an unmatched standard of living, Galaxy Realty embraces this new journey, ensuring their legacy of grandeur and artistry transcends borders and continues to inspire awe worldwide.

name: Pinnacle Developers
description:
What sets  apart is not just a belief in seeking out the highest-form of private living, it’s putting the ‘best’ in boutique. It’s a deep bond of commitment and unique shared beliefs that
unite their founders and the rest of  at Pinnacle.Luxury real estate isn’t just about the properties themselves – it’s about the experience of purchasing and residing in them. This means going above and beyond to provide impeccable service and personalised attention at every stage. Integrity means being held to the high standards of honesty, transparency, and ethical standards. They act with truth and accuracy, they honour their commitments, and prioritise long-term relationships over short-term gains.Trust is the ultimate currency in their line of work, as clients entrust developers with their dreams, investments, and aspirations. They know that trust is not just earned but nurtured through every interaction and transaction, cementing their reputation as a trusted advisor and partner in luxury real estate.unite their founders and the rest of  at Pinnacle.Luxury real estate isn’t just about the properties themselves – it’s about the experience of purchasing and residing in them. This means going above and beyond to provide impeccable service and personalised attention at every stage. Integrity means being held to the high standards of honesty, transparency, and ethical standards. They act with truth and accuracy, they honour their commitments, and prioritise long-term relationships over short-term gains.Trust is the ultimate currency in their line of work, as clients entrust developers with their dreams, investments, and aspirations. They know that trust is not just earned but nurtured through every interaction and transaction, cementing their reputation as a trusted advisor and partner in luxury real estate.

name: Enso Delevopment
description:
Step into the world of ENSO, where every structure tells a story of elegance, innovation, and sustainability. Company philosophy, rooted in the Zen concept of 'Enso,' symbolises completeness, strength, and the beauty of imperfection, guiding their journey towards creating havens that inspire and uplift. Within their meticulously designed spaces, luxury intertwines with purpose.
At ENSO, integrity is their compass, guiding every decision we make. Company believe in progress with a conscience, where ethical considerations are as important as aesthetic appeal. It's this unwavering commitment to quality and ethics that sets they apart, earning the trust of discerning clients and shaping the cities of tomorrow.

name: Al Seeb
description:
With world-class service, top-notch realtors and a strong belief in offering a choice of luxury spaces at affordable prices, their professionalism and practical outlook translate into projects that hold the future of real estate. Over the past 29 years, the company has built a reputation based on excellence in residential projects, hotels, shopping centres and commercial spaces.

Embodying the vision of the parent company, Al Safeer Group, a team of 3,500 professionals under the aegis of the founding Chairman and CEO, Mr J.P. Kalwani, ensures unmatched commitment.

The company's portfolio covers retail, shopping centres, food outlets, real estate, furniture, manufacturing, advertising, trading and more. Maintaining value for money, the client's investment is ensured through technical know-how, behind-the-scenes expertise, market research and competitive pricing.

name: NYX Real Estate Development
description: At NYX Real Estate Development, we create more than residences — we craft landmarks of modern design, refined comfort, and lasting value.For residents, our communities offer elevated living with curated amenities that balance wellness, convenience, and connection.For investors, they present strong opportunities in one of the region’s most resilient markets.Blending timeless design, strategic locations, and sustainable innovation, NYX set the benchmark for luxury living and trusted investment

name: LMD
description: Since its inception in 2007, LMD has been on a dedicated mission to craft transformative experiences through thriving communities and integrated destinations that put you and innovation at heart. The company boasts a successful selection of projects, spanning first and second homes, as well as iconic mixed-use developments with a strong foothold in Dubai, Spain and Greece.

name: SIDO Development
description:
Sido Development is a distinguished real estate developer operating in the UAE, the UK, and Romania, known for its focus on innovation, sustainability, and quality. With over 40 years of experience and a portfolio that includes ownership of more than 1,000 rental properties, Sido brings expertise and credibility to the Dubai market.

Their first major development in Dubai, Waref Residences in Jumeirah Village Circle (JVC), demonstrates their commitment to crafting modern living spaces. The project features a seven-story building with thoughtfully designed apartments, premium finishes, and a wide range of amenities including a swimming pool, gym, yoga lawn, outdoor cinema, BBQ area, and landscaped gardens — all intended to enhance resident lifestyle and foster community connection.

Sido aims to redefine urban living by combining accessibility, smart design, and strong return potential. Waref Residences boasts strategic access to major destinations like Dubai Marina and Downtown Dubai (within 15–18 minutes), while offering affordability without compromising on luxury. The developer places sustainability and eco-conscious practices at the core of its projects to create spaces that are both elegant and responsible.

name: Baraka Real Estate Development
description: Baraka Real Estate Development was established as a strategic partnership between Bin Ham Properties and Caphy Properties and with an ambitious vision to construct distinguished projects that include residential, commercial properties and entertainment destinations in various parts of the region and abroad so that its units are distinguished by their modern designs and modern facilities and at competitive prices to improve the quality and enrichment of its customers lives.

name: NABNI
description:
NABNI is a distinguished Emirati real estate developer dedicated to redefining luxury living through visionary design, innovation, and meticulous craftsmanship. With an unwavering commitment to excellence, the company creates living spaces that go beyond conventional standards, seamlessly blending form, function, and sustainability. Each project reflects NABNI’s customer-centric approach, ensuring that every residence is thoughtfully designed to align with the unique aspirations and lifestyles of its residents.




Rooted in integrity and innovation, NABNI continues to reshape the real estate landscape by crafting homes that transcend expectations. The developer’s vision is to set new benchmarks in luxury living by delivering residences that combine elegance, modernity, and long-term value. Through its dedication to quality and forward-thinking design, NABNI stands as a trusted name in the industry, offering a refined and sophisticated living experience in the UAE’s most sought-after locations.

name: Premier Choice International
description: At Premier Choice International, they setting the standard for excellence in real estate development by delivering seamless solutions for all property needs. With their forward-thinking approach, company leading the way in making real estate stress-free for esteemed clientele.

name: Matrix Development
description: Matrix Real Estate Development LLC is a prestigious joint venture that brings together the expertise and resources of four industry leaders in the UAE construction sector. With a commitment to excellence, we transform visions into reality, creating luxurious and innovative living spaces that stand the test of time.

name: Elton Real Estate Development
description:
Elton Real Estate Development is a visionary property developer based in Dubai, known for crafting residential experiences that reflect both elegance and emotional connection. With roots in Mumbai and a growing presence in the UAE, Elton is not just a builder of homes — it is a curator of lifestyle, driven by ambition, artistry, and a refined architectural perspective. The company focuses on boutique developments that celebrate design, tranquility, and elevated urban living.




Each Elton project reflects a dedication to quality, timeless aesthetics, and purposeful living. By blending modern sophistication with natural harmony, Elton creates communities that foster well-being, beauty, and belonging. From thoughtfully composed interiors to wellness-driven amenities, the company designs spaces where luxury is not only seen, but felt — shaping homes that inspire, comfort, and endure.

name: Union Properties
description: Union Properties is driven by four core values that define their approach: prioritizing the growth and well-being of their people, fostering a culture of care and innovation; building strong relationships through integrity, reliability, and transparent communication; adhering to ethical practices that positively impact communities and promote sustainability; and consistently pursuing excellence with a commitment to high standards and quality. Their focus on innovation and determination ensures they explore new possibilities and find creative solutions to challenges.

name: Mill Hill Riviera Development
description: Mill Hill is an outstanding real estate developer with an impressive 20 years of experience in both the UK and UAE markets. Their portfolio includes a wide range of high-end projects, from 5-star hotels in central London to expensive apartment blocks in Birmingham, as well as luxury villas on the Palm Jumeirah. With extensive business connections in the UAE, Mill Hill works with some of the most innovative design studios and architects, ensuring that every project embodies excellence and sophistication. As they embark on new projects, their flagship project Allegro promises to set new standards for luxury living in the Dubai islands.

name: Dar Al Karama
description: At Dar Al Karama, we are more than just a real estate development company; we are a culmination of four decades of experience, a testament to family values, and a commitment to shaping the future of living spaces in Dubai. Established in 1985, our main business has been an integral part of Dubai's growth and infrastructure development in the main communities like: DownTown, Dubai Hills, Jumeirah Palm, Damac Hills and many others. With deep roots in this dynamic city, we have expanded our horizons to create Dar Al Karama Real Estate ( DAK ), a visionary real estate development company. We take pride in not only building homes but also in nurturing communities where families can thrive. With a legacy of excellence and a future filled with promise, Dar Al Karama welcomes you to discover a new standard of living in Dubai

name: Al Mizan
description:
Al Mizan is a distinguished real estate developer committed to creating environments that promote well-being, fulfillment, and long-term growth. Since its inception in 1998, the company has prioritized investor success, ensuring that every project is meticulously designed and strategically located for maximum returns. With a focus on quality, flexibility, and sustainability, Al Mizan blends modern design with nature, delivering high-end yet cost-effective properties that stand the test of time.




Beyond constructing homes, Al Mizan shapes positive lifestyles, crafting spaces that bring happiness, comfort, and long-term value. The company operates with transparency and ethical business practices, fostering trust with investors and clients alike. By taking a 360-degree approach—from land acquisition to property management—Al Mizan ensures seamless integration and superior client satisfaction. Rooted in excellence and innovation, the company continues to redefine urban living while staying true to its vision of building not just properties, but brighter futures.

name: AGN Skyline Developers
description: AGN Skyline Developers is a Dubai-based property developer specializing in mid- to high-end residential projects, with a strong focus on luxury apartments offered at competitive prices. Guided by a vision of elegance and innovation, the company crafts living spaces where modern architecture meets timeless comfort. Each project is a harmonious blend of form and function, thoughtfully designed to elevate everyday living into a refined experience. With meticulous attention to detail and a passion for quality, AGN Skyline Developers transforms emerging neighborhoods into vibrant, sought-after communities. Their developments are more than just residences - they are expressions of lifestyle, ambition, and forward-thinking urban design.

name: Ora Developers
description: Ora is a developer with an ethos to deliver unmatched experiences that embody human aspirations of self-fulfillment, and the pinnacle of happiness through a sensorial approach that can only be described as a surreal yet perfect moment of lifetime achievement in luxury living. Reimagining time, their projects are often likened to a complicated luxury timepiece that offer perfect blends of intricate detail which can only result in a flawless breathtaking moment of awe-inspiring serenity of luxury living. Ora is a leading name in the field of designing and developing luxury lifestyle destinations in unique locations. They bring world-class expertise, exceptional attention to detail and visionary ideas to every landmark project they work on.

name: ACW Holdings
description: ACW Holdings, established in 2004, is a UK-based property developer specializing in high-yield investments in the United Arab Emirates. With offices in Leeds and London, the company is registered with RERA and offers real estate development and related services.

name: RMG Limited
description: RMG Limited is a real estate development company operating in Dubai's property sector, specializing in the construction of residential projects. The company is best known for its development of Niloofar Tower, located in the Culture Village area.RMG Limited began its operations in 2008, focusing on the development of residential properties in Dubai. Currently, the company's projects are represented within the city of Dubai. Developer's Projects: Niloofar Tower

name: Shapoorji Pallonji
description: For over 150 years, Shapoorji Pallonji has been at the forefront of construction and engineering. Many of our early projects have stood the test of time and serve as monuments to our age-old legacy.It’s our ability to take on projects of scale and complexity and our ability to deliver consistently that has helped us build a reputation amongst our partners and customers. It is one of “Trust and Transparency,” and these words have echoed across our hallways for generations.

name: Lokhandwala Builders
description: Lokhandwala Builders International LLC is a distinguished real estate developer committed to delivering exceptional properties that harmoniously blend aesthetic appeal with functionality. With a focus on innovation and quality, the company strives to create residences that not only meet but exceed the expectations of modern urban living. Their dedication to excellence is evident in every project, reflecting a deep understanding of architectural finesse and customer needs.

name: Kayan Al Arabiah Developer
description:
Kayan Al Arabiah is a prominent real estate developer based in Sharjah, United Arab Emirates, dedicated to crafting innovative residential and commercial spaces. With a focus on blending modern luxury with community-centric values, Kayan aims to redefine living standards in the UAE. Their developments emphasize quality, sustainability, and a harmonious balance between urban convenience and tranquil living environments. Notable projects include Camila and Kayan Signature Villas, both located in the sought-after Uptown Al Zahia community, offering elegant designs and spacious interiors that cater to discerning homeowners. 




Kayan's reputation is built on a track record of delivering high-quality projects on time, ensuring customer satisfaction and solid returns on investment. Their diverse portfolio encompasses various types of developments, reflecting their extensive experience in the real estate market. By prioritizing clear contracts and energy-efficient designs, Kayan ensures transparency and sustainability in all their ventures. Their commitment to excellence positions them as a trusted name in the region's property development sector.

name: OCTA Development
description:
OCTA Development is a forward-driven real estate development company based in the UAE, known for its design-led approach and commitment to elevating everyday living. With a philosophy rooted in innovation, quality, and purposeful design, OCTA reimagines residential and mixed-use spaces that combine architectural distinction with practical elegance. Their signature concept, Life², reflects a mission to amplify the ordinary into the extraordinary—enhancing every detail of modern living through thoughtful planning and refined execution.

The company’s projects are crafted to deliver more than just homes—they offer curated lifestyles. name: Dubai International Financial Centre
description: The Dubai International Financial Centre (DIFC) is a special economic zone in Dubai covering 110 ha (272 acres), established in 2004 as a financial hub for companies operating throughout the Middle East, Africa, and South Asia (MEASA) markets.DIFC is regulated by the Dubai Financial Services Authority, an independent regulator exclusive to the zone, and by its own court system, DIFC Courts, separate from the Emirate of Dubai's legal system and that of the federal government of the UAE. DIFC follows the common law framework and operates in English.DIFC is one of Dubai's independent free zones; it offers companies 100% ownership without the need for a local partner. The freezone houses financial institutions, and wealth funds in addition to retail and hotel space dedicated to the free zones.DIFC offers clients a 50-year guarantee of zero taxes on corporate income and profits, complemented by the UAE's network of double taxation treaties.
